%22esnodgrass%40insider.com%20(Erin%20Snodgrass)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcargo-ship-ran-aground-officer-snoring-loudly-watch-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Says%20It's%20Taking%20Khalistani%20Terrorist's%20Foiled%20Murder%20Plot%20%26quot%3BVery%20Seriously%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesperson%2C%20John%20Kirby%2C%20stressed%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20US%20continues%20to%20improve%20its%20strategic%20partnership%20with%20India.%20On%20the%20other%20side%2C%20he%20added%20that%20the%20US%20%26quot%3Btakes%20this%20very%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20referring%20to%20the%20indictment%20by%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20against%20an%20Indian%20in%20an%20alleged%20foiled%20assassination%20plot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20speaking%20at%20a%20press%20briefing%2C%20Kirby%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia%20remains%20a%20strategic%20partner%2C%20and%20we%20are%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20work%20to%20improve%20and%20strengthen%20that%20strategic%20partnership%20with%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20US%20Justice%20Department%20indictment%20of%20an%20Indian%20national%20in%20an%20alleged%20foiled%20assassination%20plot%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Kirby%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20take%20this%20very%20seriously.%20These%20allegations%20and%20this%20investigation%2C%20we%20take%20very%20seriously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20we%20are%20glad%20to%20see%20that%20India%20is%20also%20taking%20it%20seriously%20by%20announcing%20their%20%26quot%3Bown%20efforts%20to%20investigate%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20clear%20that%20we%20want%20to%20see%20anybody%20that's%20responsible%20for%20these%20alleged%20crimes%20to%20be%20held%20properly%20accountable...%2C%26quot%3B%20Kirby%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20unsealed%20an%20indictment%20against%20an%20Indian%20national%20for%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20a%20foiled%20plot%20to%20assassinate%20a%20US-based%20leader%20of%20the%20Sikh%20Separatist%20Movement%20and%20a%20citizen%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Justice%20Department%20has%20claimed%20that%20an%20Indian%20government%20employee%20(named%20CC-1)%2C%20who%20was%20not%20identified%20in%20the%20indictment%20filed%20in%20a%20federal%20court%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20recruited%20an%20Indian%20national%20named%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20to%20hire%20a%20hitman%20to%20allegedly%20carry%20out%20the%20assassination%20of%20the%20Sikh%20Separatist%2C%20which%20was%20foiled%20by%20US%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Justice%20Department%20claimed%20that%20Gupta%2C%20is%20an%20associate%20of%20CC-1%2C%20and%20has%20described%20his%20involvement%20in%20international%20narcotics%20and%20weapons%20trafficking%20in%20his%20communications%20with%20CC-1.%20The%20indictment%20claims%20CC%20-1%20directed%20the%20assassination%20plot%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20in%20a%20news%20briefing%20the%20MEA%20on%20Thursday%20said%20that%20a%20case%20filed%20against%20an%20individual%20in%20a%20US%20court%20and%20allegedly%20linking%20him%20to%20an%20Indian%20official%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bmatter%20of%20concern%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20contrary%20to%20government%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20share%20any%20further%20information%20on%20such%20security%20matters.%20As%20regards%20the%20case%20against%20an%20individual%20that%20has%20been%20filed%20in%20a%20US%20court%20allegedly%20linking%20him%20to%20an%20Indian%20official%2C%20this%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern.%20We%20have%20said%20and%20let%20me%20reiterate%20that%20this%20is%20contrary%20to%20government%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26q