lies%2C%20food%2C%20and%20fuel%20into%20Gaza%20after%20fierce%20combat%20and%20bombardments%20sparked%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fblinken-calls-on-israel-to-create-safe-zones-for-gaza-civilians-4622936%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHamas's%20bloody%20October%207%20attacks%20on%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20over%20the%20last%20week%20the%20very%20positive%20development%20of%20hostages%20coming%20home%2C%20being%20reunited%20with%20their%20families%2C%26quot%3B%20Blinken%20said%20earlier%20at%20a%20meeting%20with%20Israeli%20President%20Isaac%20Herzog%20in%20Tel%20Aviv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20also%20enabled%20an%20increase%20in%20humanitarian%20assistance%20to%20go%20to%20innocent%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%20who%20need%20it%20desperately.%20So%20this%20process%20is%20producing%20results.%20It's%20important%2C%20and%20we%20hope%20that%20it%20can%20continue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20told%20Netanyahu%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bimperative%26quot%3B%20to%20protect%20civilians%20in%20southern%20Gaza%20%26quot%3Bbefore%20any%20military%20operations%20there%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20truce%2C%20Israeli%20ground%20and%20air%20forces%20had%20pounded%20Gaza%2C%20forcing%20an%20estimated%201.7%20million%20people%20--%20around%2080%20percent%20of%20the%20Hamas-run%20territory's%20population%20--%20to%20leave%20their%20homes%20and%20limiting%20the%20entry%20of%20food%2C%20water%2C%20medicine%20and%20fuel%2C%20according%20to%20the%20UN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20four-day%20truce%20has%20been%20extended%20for%20three%20days%20following%20work%20by%20international%20mediators%2C%20led%20by%20Qatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20however%20vowed%20to%20continue%20with%20its%20offensive%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%20once%20the%20truce%20process%20has%20run%20its%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20swore...%20to%20eliminate%20Hamas%2C%20and%20nothing%20will%20stop%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20said%20in%20a%20video%20released%20by%20his%20office%2C%20after%20meeting%20with%20Blinken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20freed%20two%20Israeli%20women%20hostages%20in%20the%20latest%20round%20of%20exchanges%20under%20the%20existing%20truce%2C%20followed%20by%20six%20more%20hostages%20later%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQatari%20officials%20mediating%20in%20the%20conflict%20said%20those%20eight%20people%20included%20nationals%20of%20Mexico%2C%20Russia%20and%20Uruguay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20others%2C%20Russian-Israeli%20dual%20citizens%2C%20were%20released%20on%20Wednesday%20night%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20group%20of%2010%20scheduled%20for%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20exchange%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-releases-30-palestinian-prisoners-in-latest-exchange-4623003%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E30%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20were%20released%20from%20Israeli%20jails%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20prison%20authorities%20said%2C%20including%2023%20minors%20and%20seven%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20truce%20began%20on%20November%2024%2C%2080%20Israeli%20hostages%20and%20240%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20have%20been%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2020%20foreigners%2C%20most%20of%20them%20Thais%20living%20in%20Israel%2C%20have%20been%20freed%20outside%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu's%20office%20named%20the%20first%20two%20hostages%20released%20Thursday%20as%20French-Israeli%20dual%20national%20Mia%20Shem%2C%2021%2C%20and%20Amit%20Soussana%2C%2040.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShem%20tearfully%20hugged%20her%20mother%20Keren%20and%20her%20brother%20as%20she%20arrived%20at%20an%20Israeli%20air%20base%20following%20her%20release%2C%20video%20distributed%20by%20the%20Israel%20government's