%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20two%20Israeli%20soldiers%20were%20slightly%20injured%20in%20a%20ramming%20attack%20on%20a%20checkpoint%20in%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20army%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20assailant%20had%20also%20been%20%26quot%3Bshot%20and%20neutralised%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701398160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fdofccdsg_israel-attack-in-gaza-reuters_625x300_24_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-willing-to-extend-truce-as-us-urges-israel-for-gaza-safe-zones-4623029%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hamas%20is%20willing%20to%20further%20extend%20a%20truce%20for%20hostage%20and%20prisoner%20exchanges%2C%20a%20source%20close%20to%20the%20group%20said%20Thursday%2C%20and%20the%20United%20States%20urged%20Israel%20to%20set%20up%20safe%20zones%20for%20Gaza%20civilians%20as%20a%20pause%20in%20their%20deadly%20war%20neared%20expiry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-willing-to-extend-truce-as-us-urges-israel-for-gaza-safe-zones-4623029%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-willing-to-extend-truce-as-us-urges-israel-for-gaza-safe-zones-4623029%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-willing-to-extend-truce-as-us-urges-israel-for-gaza-safe-zones-4623029%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20CAG%20Performance%20Audit%20of%20MGNREGA%20for%2010%20Years%20Poses%20Serious%20Questions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12153943%2FEe5Ey1CUwAMmwIG.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20(CAG)%20of%20India%20has%20not%20conducted%20a%20Union%20level%20performance%20audit%20of%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Generation%20Act%20(MGNREGA)%20since%202013.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20CAG%20reports%20available%20on%20its%20website%2C%20a%20performance%20audit%20of%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20scheme%20%E2%80%93%20which%20guarantees%20100%20days%20of%20work%20to%20rural%20households%20every%20year%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewas%20last%20conducted%20in%202013.%20The%20scheme%20was%20taken%20up%20for%20audit%20by%20the%20CAG%20at%20the%20national%20level%20in%202016%2C%20but%20not%20as%20a%20performance%20audit%20but%20only%20to%20examine%20the%20Social%20Audit%20Units%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ewhich%20are%20meant%20to%20detect%20any%20cases%20of%20malpractice%20%E2%80%93%20under%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20learnt%20that%20while%20the%202013%20report%20was%20comprehensive%20and%20covered%20the%20MGNREGA%E2%80%99s%20implementation%20across%20the%20country%2C%20there%20was%20a%20plan%20after%20that%20to%20cover%20the%20social%20impact%20of%20the%20scheme%2C%20which%20was%20done%20in%20the%202016%20report.%20However%2C%20after%20that%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20elaborate%20report%20on%20MGNREGA.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESources%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20principally%20a%20performance%20audit%20of%20every%20scheme%20is%20done%20after%20every%20five%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAbout%207-8%20schemes%20are%20earmarked%20every%20year%20for%20audit.%20Unless%20there%20is%20a%20request%20from%20the%20government%20or%20the%20CAG%20is%20particular%20about%20one%2C%20in%20routine%20course%20a%20scheme%20may%20come%20up%20again%20for%20performance%20audit%20in%20ten%20years%20also.%20So%2C%20as%20it%20(MGNREGA)%20was%20done%20in%202016%2C%20there%20is%20a%20likelihood%20that%20it%20may%20come%20up%20again%20in%202026%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20source%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CRegular%20audit%20is%20done%20every%20year%20which%20is%20called%20transactional%20audit%20through%20which%20we%20cover%20all%20states%20and%20all%20schemes.%20But%20as%20regards%20performance%20audit%2C%20it%20depends%20on%20the%20gravity%20or%20suppose%20a%20high%20court%20or%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20taken%20issue%20or%20someone%20has%20filed%20in%20the%20PAC%20(Public%20Accounts%20Committee)%20about%20where%20the%20money%20is%20going%20then%20the%20CAG%20may%20be%20directed%20to%20conduct%20an%20audit%20of%20the%20scheme%20but%20otherwise%20CAG%20takes%20a%20decision%20on%20its%20own%20and%20in%20routine%20course%20it%20can%20take%20any%20time.%20If%20a%20certain%20aspect%20of%20a%20scheme%20is%20being%20taken%20up%20for%20audit%20(like%20the%202016%20CAG%20report%20on%20MGNREGS%E2%80%99%20Social%20Audit%20Units)%20that%20means%20that%20the%20scheme%20has%20been%20covered.%20It%20may%20not%20cover%20all%20aspects%2C%20but%20even%20if%20two%20or%20three%20aspects%20are%20covered%20it%20means%20that%20we%20have%20touched%20that%20scheme.%20There%20are%20hundreds%20of%20government%20schemes%2C%20even%20in%20the%20cycle%20of%20five%20years%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20cover%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20CAG%20office%20for%20a%20response.%20This%20report%20will%20be%20updated%20if%20and%20when%20a%20response%20is%20received.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20CAG%20audit%20reports%20are%20important%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECAG%20reports%20have%20been%20of%20special%20interest%20since%20the%20UPA%20government%20came%20under%20fire%20for%20alleged%20scams%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2F2g-accused-acquitted-happened-scam-wasnt%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2G%20spectrum%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0and%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcoalgate-scam-ex-coal-secretary-h-c-gupta-sentenced-to-three-years-in-jail%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecoal%20block%20allocations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20monsoon%20session%20of%20parliament%20that%20ended%20in%20August%2C%20the%20CAG%20presented%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_BDqVanVhZo%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etwelve%20reports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20revealed%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fayushman-bharat-cag-report-pmjay-corruption%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecorruption%20and%20irregularities%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20functioning%20of%20several%20Union%20government%20ministries%20and%20departments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20CAG%20Office%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fofficers-cag-reports-ayushman-bharat-bharatmala-transferred%5C%22%3Etransferring%3C%2Fa%3E%20three%20officers%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20had%20worked%20on%20the%20most%20damaging%20reports%2C%20the%20opposition%20parties%20have%20accused%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcag-officers-transfers-opposition-accuses-modi-government-intimidation%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eintimidation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20officers%20were%20in%20charge%20of%20audit%20reports%20that%20exposed%20corruption%20in%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20project%20and%20Ayushman%20Bharat.%20A%20third%20officer%20who%20had%20initiated%20the%20audit%20of%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20report%20was%20also%20transferred.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20also%20reported%20that%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-after-verbal-orders-to-stop-all-field-work-officers-ask-for-written-orders%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Everbal%20orders%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cspan%3E%20were%20issued%20by%20the%20CAG%20to%20stop%20field%20audit%20work%20that%20is%20crucial%20for%20auditing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CAG%20has%20termed%20these%20reports%20as%20%E2%80%9Cerroneous%20and%20baseless.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20CAG%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-after-verbal-orders-to-stop-all-field-work-officers-ask-for-written-orders%5C%22%3EAfter%20Verbal%20Orders%20to%20%E2%80%98Stop%20all%20Field%20Work%E2%80%99%2C%20Officers%20Ask%20for%20Written%20Orders%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20constitutional%20authority%2C%20the%20CAG%20is%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcag.gov.in%2Fag%2Fchhattisgarh%2Fen%2Fpage-ag-chhattisgarh-duties-and-powers%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20sole%20authority%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20constitution%20entrusts%20the%20responsibility%20of%20auditing%20the%20accounts%20of%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CAG%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcag.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fguidelines%2FPA-Guidelines2014-05-updated-062f4aa3d0af371-98564945.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eperformance%20audits%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20examine%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20an%20activity%2C%20programme%20or%20organisation%20operates%20economically%2C%20efficiently%20and%20effectively.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMGNREGA%E2%80%99s%20shrinking%20budget%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMGNREGA%2C%20a%20one%20of%20its%20kind%20right%20to%20work%20act%20in%20the%20world%2C%20was%20enacted%20in%202006%20with%20the%20objective%20of%20enhancing%20livelihood%20security%20in%20rural%20areas%20by%20providing%20at%20least%20100%20days%20of%20guaranteed%20wage%20employment%20in%20a%20financial%20year.%20This%20is%20guaranteed%20to%20every%20household%20whose%20adult%20members%20volunteer%20for%20unskilled%20manual%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20initially%20came%20into%20force%20in%20200%20districts%20from%20February%202%2C%202006%20and%20was%20expanded%20to%20cover%20all%20rural%20areas%20by%20April%201%2C%202008.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scheme%20is%20implemented%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Rural%20Development%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Rural%C2%A0%20Development.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Ffiles%2Fbudget%2Fbudget_parliament%2F2023%2FDFG_RuralDev_23-24.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eanalysis%20by%20PRS%20Legislative%20Research%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3Cspan%3E%20in%202023-24%2C%20MGNREGS%20(38%25)%20gets%20the%20highest%20budgetary%20allocation%20in%20the%20department%E2%80%99s%20accounting.%20The%20rural%20development%20department%20also%20implements%20other%20major%20social%20sector%20schemes%20such%20as%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Gram%20Sadak%20Yojana%20(PMGSY)%20and%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awas%20Yojana-Gramin%20(PMAY-G).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202023%20budget%2C%20the%20MGNREGS%20was%20allocated%20Rs%2060%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnikhil-dey-mgnrega-budget-cut-2023%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EConcerns%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20have%20been%20raised%20that%20the%20allocation%20to%20the%20MGNREGS%20has%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fnrega-budget-allocation-2023-24%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edeclined%20by%2033%25%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20revised%20estimates%20of%202022-23.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EUnion-level%20CAG%20reports%20on%20MGNREGA%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CAG%E2%80%99s%202013%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcag.gov.in%2Fen%2Faudit-report%2Fdownload%2F704%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ecovered%20the%20period%20from%20April%202007%20to%20March%202012.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrior%20to%20that%2C%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncst.nic.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fdocuments%2Fimportant_circulars_reports_for_reference%2FCAGrep722009340.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efirst%20performance%20audit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eof%20the%20scheme%20was%20undertaken%20in%202007-08%20and%20covered%20the%20period%20from%20February%202006%20to%20March%202007.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%202013%20report%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20then%20UPA%20government%20and%20noted%20that%20there%20had%20been%20a%20%E2%80%9Csignificant%20decline%E2%80%9D%20in%20per%20rural%20household%20employment%20generation%20in%20the%20previous%20two%20years%20and%20%E2%80%9Csubstantial%20decline%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20proportion%20of%20works%20completed.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20Bihar%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20together%20account%20for%2046%25%20of%20the%20rural%20poor%2C%20utilised%20only%20about%2020%25%20of%20the%20Central%20Scheme%20funds%20which%20indicated%20that%20the%20correlation%20between%20poverty%20levels%20and%20implementation%20of%20MGNREGA%20was%20not%20very%20high.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmonitoring%20at%20the%20central%20level%20was%20unsatisfactory.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%202016%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcag.gov.in%2Fwebroot%2Fuploads%2Fdownload_audit_report%2F2016%2FUnion_Civil_MGNREG_SOCIAL_Audit_Report_8_2016.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eexamined%20the%20functioning%20of%20Social%20Audit%20Units%20under%20MGNREGA.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESocial%20audit%20is%20described%20in%20the%20report%20as%20verification%20of%20the%20implementation%20of%20a%20programme%2Fscheme%20and%20its%20results%20by%20the%20community%20with%20the%20active%20involvement%20of%20the%20primary%20stakeholders.%20It%20is%20mandated%20under%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Audit%20of%20Schemes%20Rules%2C%202011.%20The%20rules%20were%20framed%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Rural%20Development%20in%20consultation%20with%20the%20CAG.%20The%20rules%20provide%20for%20the%20state%20government%20to%20facilitate%20identification%20and%20creation%20of%20independent%20organisations%20i.e.%20Social%20Audit%20Units%20(SAU)%2C%20process%20of%20conducting%20these%20audits%20and%20obligations%20of%20persons%20related%20to%20the%20audits.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20report%20noted%20several%20irregularities%20including%20that%20SAU%20had%20not%20been%20set%20up%20in%20seven%20states%2C%20while%20in%20eight%20states%20they%20were%20set%20up%20but%20not%20functional.%20It%20also%20noted%20a%20shortage%20of%20resource%20persons%20to%20carry%20out%20such%20Social%20Audits%2C%20among%20other%20findings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeven%20years%20since%20this%20report%2C%20the%20CAG%20is%20yet%20to%20conduct%20a%20performance%20audit%20of%20the%20MGNREGA%20scheme%20as%20a%20whole%20or%20any%20aspect%20of%20the%20scheme%20at%20the%20Union%20level.%20A%20recent%20media%20report%20said%20that%20the%20SAU%E2%80%99s%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fabysmally-low-recovery-rates-in-mgnrega-corruption-cases-flagged-by-auditors%2Farticle67357388.ece%5C%22%3Eailing%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0because%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ethey%20are%20fund-starved%20and%20do%20not%20have%20trained%20or%20adequate%20personnel%20working%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F15142032%2F7655150258_30d4e48fdc_b.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F15142032%2F7655150258_30d4e48fdc_b.jpg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F15142032%2F7655150258_30d4e48fdc_b-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F15142032%2F7655150258_30d4e48fdc_b-768x512.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-232536%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMGNREGA%20workers.%20Women%2FGaganjit%20Singh%2FFlickr%20CC%20BY-NC-ND%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%9CPerformance%20audit%20depends%20on%20risk%20assessment%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESubhash%20Chandra%20Pandey%2C%20a%20former%20IA%26amp%3BAS%20officer%20who%20retired%20as%20special%20secretary%20and%20financial%20adviser%20in%20the%20Union%20ministry%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20and%20is%20at%20present%20serving%20as%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Institute%20of%20Public%20Auditors%20of%20India%20(IPAI)%2C%20said%20that%20audits%20are%20conducted%20by%20field%20offices%20in%20the%20Indian%20Audit%20and%20Accounts%20Department.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EField%20audits%20continue%20in%20block%20development%20offices%20and%20inspection%20reports%20are%20issued%20by%20State%20Accountant%20General%20offices.%20If%20major%20irregularities%20are%20found%20that%20merit%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20Parliament%20or%20state%20legislatures%2C%20these%20find%20mention%20in%20the%20CAG%20reports%20to%20the%20concerned%20legislatures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COccasionally%2C%20the%20CAG%20office%20takes%20up%20performance%20audits%20of%20major%20central%20schemes%20on%20all%20India%20basis%20and%20that%20report%20is%20sent%20to%20parliament.%20The%20MGNREGA%20performance%20audit%20in%202013%20was%20the%20second%20performance%20review.%20When%20the%20CAG%20reports%20go%20to%20the%20Parliament%2C%20these%20are%20considered%20by%20the%20Public%20Accounts%20Committee%20(PAC).%20The%20ministry%20or%20department%20concerned%20are%20supposed%20to%20submit%20Action%20Taken%20Notes%20on%20the%20CAG%20reports%20to%20the%20PAC.%20They%20are%20vetted%20by%20the%20CAG%20office%20before%20submission%20to%20the%20PAC.%20So%20it%20is%20seen%20that%20based%20on%20the%202013%20report%2C%20the%20government%20has%20taken%20several%20remedial%20actions%20to%20improve%20programme%20implementation%20in%20the%20(MGNREGA)%20programme%20to%20reduce%20the%20audit%20risks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPandey%20said%20that%20major%20systemic%20changes%20undertaken%20by%20the%20Centre%20include%20Aadhaar%20linked%20direct%20benefit%20transfer%20(DBT)%20payment%20to%20tackle%20fake%20or%20duplicate%20beneficiaries%2C%20and%20geotagging%20of%20assets%20to%20monitor%20the%20authenticity%20of%20assets%20created.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20Management%20Information%20System%20(MIS)%20done%20by%20the%20Rural%20Development%20Ministry%20to%20digitise%20the%20scheme%2C%20as%20well%20as%20bringing%20in%20DBT%20to%20beneficiaries%20to%20tackle%20diversion%20of%20funds%20have%20helped%20to%20substantially%20mitigate%20audit%20risks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBudgetary%20amounts%20can%20be%20very%20large%20(like%20Rs%2060%2C0000%20crore%20for%20MGNREGA)%20but%20from%20these%20three%20angles%20all%20related%20to%20technology%2C%20the%20system%20is%20streamlined%20and%20risks%20are%20minimised%2C%20maybe%20not%20eliminated%20altogether.%20So%20maybe%20they%20may%20have%20focused%20on%20other%20areas%20where%20risks%20are%20higher%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTaking%20up%20Performance%20Audit%20for%20a%20CAG%20report%20depends%20on%20the%20assessment%20of%20audit%20risks%20because%20the%20audit%20department%20has%20limited%20resources%20while%20the%20audit%20mandate%20is%20vast.%20So%20audit%20resource%20deployment%20depends%20on%20risk%20assessment.%20If%20the%20assessment%20for%20MGNREGA%20is%20that%20the%20central%20government%20has%20taken%20adequate%20technological%20steps%20like%20Aadhaar%2C%20geo%20tagging%20and%20DBT%20%E2%80%93%20the%20programme%E2%80%99s%20systemic%20risks%20at%20the%20top%20level%20have%20been%20addressed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20residual%20risks%20remain%20are%20at%20the%20local%20level%2C%20that%20does%20not%20merit%20bringing%20a%20report%20to%20the%20Parliament.%20That%20is%20actually%20at%20the%20panchayat%20level.%20That%20is%20why%20they%20came%20up%20with%20the%20social%20audit%20report%20to%20strengthen%20it%20as%20IAAD%20cannot%20go%20around%20covering%20all%20villages%2C%20there%20is%20just%20not%20enough%20manpower%20for%20that.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ELack%20of%20accountability%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20former%20deputy%20CAG%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20named%20said%20that%20the%20CAG%20Act%20gives%20the%20CAG%20almost%20an%20open%20mandate%20to%20determine%20what%20and%20to%20audit%2C%20including%20government%20expenditure%2C%20schemes%2C%20and%20programmes%2C%20both%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20states%2C%20and%20to%20some%20extent%20in%20local%20bodies.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20answer%20%5Bto%20why%20an%20important%20scheme%20like%20MGNREGA%20is%20not%20getting%20audited%5D%20lies%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20is%20no%20accountability%20at%20the%20moment%20for%20the%20person%20who%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20the%20chief%20accountability%20officer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20CAG%20is%20not%20an%20auditor%20on%20call%20for%20the%20government.%20The%20CAG%20is%20an%20external%20auditor%20and%20can%20only%20give%20his%20opinion.%20The%20government%20has%20internal%20auditors%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cga.nic.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECGA%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(Controller%20General%20of%20Accounts%20who%20is%20responsible%20for%20exchequer%20control%20and%20internal%20audits%20of%20the%20Union%20government).%20The%20CAG%20is%20not%20a%20subordinate%20employee%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20either.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20an%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcag.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fmedia%2FDPC2014new-20201008140628.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAct%20of%20parliament%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20gives%20him%20the%20right%20to%20determine%20what%20he%20will%20audit.%20It%20is%20not%20explicitly%20mentioned%20that%20he%20should%20also%20present%20the%20basis%20on%20which%20he%20is%20exercising%20his%20right%20to%20audit%20what%20he%20will%20audit%20but%20there%20is%20a%20moral%20obligation%20as%20a%20constitutional%20officer.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAlongside%20his%20audit%20reports%20every%20year%2C%20the%20CAG%20should%20present%20his%20methodology%20of%20risk%20analysis%20through%20which%20he%20deploys%20his%20resources%20to%20various%20audit%20concerns.%20Then%20the%20question%20arises%2C%20why%20MGNREGA%20which%20is%20such%20an%20important%20scheme%20has%20not%20attracted%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20CAG.%20He%20is%20a%20public%20official%20and%20the%20taxpayer%20has%20the%20right%20to%20know%20how%20he%20is%20deploying%20his%20resources%20into%20examining%20the%20business%20of%20the%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Slowly%20but%20steadily%20killing%20MGNREGA%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EM.G.%20Devasahayam%2C%20a%20former%20IAS%20officer%2C%20said%20that%20while%20the%20MGNREGA%20is%20a%20centrally-sponsored%20scheme%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20only%20meant%20to%20provide%20monetary%20support.%20The%20implementation%20lies%20at%20the%20block%20and%20district%20level%20and%20then%20with%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20opposition%20ruled%20states%20like%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftrinamool-supporters-protest-non-release-mgnregs-pmay-funds-delhi-jantar-mantar%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWest%20Bengal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20have%20accused%20the%20Union%20government%20of%20non-release%20of%20MGNREGA%20funds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20August%2C%20the%20rural%20development%20ministry%20informed%20parliament%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20has%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fcentre-owes-6366-crore-in-mgnrega-wages-to-18-states-and-union-territories%2Farticle67146519.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epending%20payments%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20under%20the%20wage%20component%20for%20a%20total%20of%2018%20States%20and%20Union%20Territories.%20Of%20this%2C%20it%20owes%20the%20highest%20amounts%20to%20opposition%20ruled%20states%3A%20Rs%202%2C770%20crore%20is%20owed%20to%20West%20Bengal%2C%20followed%20by%20Rajasthan%20(Rs%20979%20crore)%20and%20Bihar%20(Rs%20669%20crore).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20beginning%2C%20ideologically%20this%20government%20has%20not%20been%20in%20favour%20of%20MNGREGA.%20One%20is%20that%20it%20was%20brought%20in%20by%20the%20previous%20Congress%20government%20and%20it%20was%20one%20of%20their%20flagship%20projects.%20Second%20they%20(the%20BJP%20government)%20want%20to%20emphasise%20their%20infrastructure%20flagship%20projects.%20This%20is%20why%20they%20are%20slowly%20starving%20MGNREGA%20of%20funds.%20Third%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20brought%20in%20several%20Central%20schemes%20themselves%20and%20they%20want%20to%20give%20publicity%20and%20attention%20to%20that.%20Fourth%2C%20MGNREGA%20was%20the%20outcome%20of%20people%E2%80%99s%20struggle.%20So%20there%20is%20no%20other%20reason%20apart%20from%20prejudice%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20present%20government%20to%20slowly%20and%20steadily%20kill%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Devasahayam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAuditing%20by%20the%20government%20and%20its%20agencies%20has%20its%20own%20limitations%20and%20often%20has%20a%20partisan%20approach.%20Social%20audit%20is%20by%20the%20people%20themselves%20and%20is%20much%20more%20rigid%20and%20looks%20into%20the%20actual%20aspects%20of%20the%20reach%20of%20the%20scheme.%20Social%20audit%20is%20against%20the%20grain%20of%20this%20government%20as%20it%20considers%20civil%20society%20its%20enemy.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20social%20audits.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20performance%20or%20social%20audit%20and%20want%20the%20scheme%20to%20die%20a%20natural%20or%20unnatural%20death.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20centrally%20sponsored%20schemes%20that%20have%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fopinion%2Fcag-could-have-done-better%2Farticle67533089.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enot%20been%20audited%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20since%202018%20reportedly%20include%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awas%20Yojana%20(PMAY)%2C%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jeevan%20Jyoti%20Bima%20Yojana%20(PMJJBY)%20and%20the%20PM%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20(PMJJM).