ance%20of%20COP28%20as%20a%20platform%20to%20review%20progress%20made%20under%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%20and%20chart%20a%20course%20for%20future%20climate%20action.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20climate%20talks%20in%20Dubai%20come%20at%20a%20critical%20juncture%20as%20global%20emissions%20continue%20to%20surge.%20The%20UN%20announced%20on%20Thursday%20that%202023%20is%20on%20track%20to%20be%20the%20hottest%20year%20in%20recorded%20history%2C%20highlighting%20the%20urgency%20for%20immediate%20action.%20The%20establishment%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bloss%20and%20damage%26quot%3B%20fund%2C%20long%20advocated%20for%20by%20climate-vulnerable%20nations%2C%20marked%20an%20early%20victory%20at%20COP28.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20UAE%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20(EU)%20made%20initial%20commitments%20of%20%24100%20million%20and%20%24246%20million%20respectively%20to%20the%20loss%20and%20damage%20fund%2C%20but%20they%20fall%20short%20of%20the%20%24100%20billion%20needed%20by%20developing%20nations%20to%20cope%20with%20the%20devastating%20effects%20of%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECOP28%2C%20set%20to%20become%20the%20biggest%20climate%20conference%20in%20history%2C%20will%20host%20over%20140%20heads%20of%20state%20and%20government%2C%20double%20the%20attendance%20from%20last%20year's%20COP27.%20These%20high-level%20leaders%20will%20deliver%20speeches%20throughout%20Friday%20and%20Saturday%2C%20with%20Britain's%20King%20Charles%20III%20officially%20opening%20the%20event%20with%20a%20ceremonial%20address.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20UAE%20hopes%20to%20spearhead%20an%20agreement%20to%20triple%20renewable%20energy%20capacity%20and%20double%20the%20annual%20pace%20of%20energy%20efficiency%20improvements%20by%202030.%20During%20the%20crucial%20negotiations%20from%20November%2030%20to%20December%2012%2C%20experts%20have%20warned%20that%20forging%20trust%20could%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20formidable%20obstacle.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAs%20the%20conference%20commenced%2C%20delegates%20observed%20a%20minute's%20silence%20to%20pay%20their%20respects%20to%20the%20innocent%20lives%20lost%20in%20Gaza.%20On%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20summit%2C%20Israeli%20President%20Isaac%20Herzog%20met%20with%20his%20UAE%20counterpart%2C%20Sheikh%20Mohammed%20bin%20Zayed%20Al%20Nahyan.%20Palestinian%20President%20Mahmud%20Abbas%20was%20supposed%20to%20attend%20the%20COP28%20but%20his%20office%20said%20the%20Palestinian%20foreign%20minister%20would%20attend%20instead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDespite%20holding%20the%20distinction%20of%20being%20the%20world's%20two%20largest%20polluters%2C%20the%20United%20States%20and%20China's%20leaders%20are%20not%20attending%20the%20COP28.%20However%2C%20in%20a%20rare%20display%20of%20unity%2C%20both%20nations%20have%20issued%20a%20joint%20climate%20declaration%20ahead%20of%20the%20conference.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701394200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fm5ihvpfg_pm-modi-cop28-_625x300_01_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcop28-dubai-un-climate-conference-pm-modi-in-dubai-for-cop28-as-200-nations-reach-historic-climate-agreement-4623038%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20historic%20decision%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%202023%20United%20Nations%20Climate%20Change%20Conference%20in%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20nearly%20200%20nations%20reached%20an%20agreement%20to%20establish%20a%20fund%20to%20assist%20countries%20grappling%20with%20the%20effects%20of%20global%20warming.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcop28-dubai-un-climate-conference-pm-modi-in-dubai-for-cop28-as-200-nations-reach-historic-climate-agreement-4623038%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcop28-dubai-un-climate-conference-pm-modi-in-dubai-for-cop28-as-200-nations-reach-histo