r%20center.%20And%2C%20perhaps%20most%20impressively%2C%20he's%20maintained%20his%20high%20level%20of%20play%20even%20in%20the%20seasons%20after%20he%20suffered%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fvideo-dak-prescott-ankle-injury-2020-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecatastrophic%20compound%20ankle%20fracture%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20ended%20his%202020%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHe's%20played%20his%20way%20into%20generational%20wealth%20via%20several%20massive%20NFL%20contracts.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221777%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dak%20Prescott%20of%20the%20Dallas%20Cowboys%20warms%20up%20prior%20to%20a%20game%20against%20the%20San%20Francisco%2049ers%20in%20the%20NFC%20Wild%20Card%20Playoff%20game%20at%20AT%26amp%3BT%20Stadium%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6567b89cfe5bc6545ebd8ad4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDak%20Prescott.%3Cp%3EGetty%2FTom%20Pennington%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPrescott's%20success%20on%20the%20field%20has%20translated%20to%20incredible%20financial%20success%20off%20of%20it.%20But%2C%20at%20least%20relatively%20speaking%2C%20he%20was%20not%20making%20the%20big%20bucks%20in%20the%20earliest%20years%20of%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20quarterback%20signed%20a%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0again%2C%20relatively%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0modest%20four-year%2C%20%242%2C723%2C393%20entry-level%20contract%20with%20the%20Cowboys%20ahead%20of%20his%20rookie%20season.%20The%20deal%20came%20with%20a%20%24383%2C393%20signing%20bonus%2C%20all%20of%20which%20was%20guaranteed%2C%20per%20Spotrac.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20by%202020%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0his%20fifth%20year%20as%20an%20NFL%20starter%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Prescott%20was%20in%20the%20market%20for%20a%20much%20more%20lucrative%20deal.%20And%20in%20March%20of%20that%20year%2C%20well%20before%20training%20camp%20began%2C%20Dallas%20placed%20a%20franchise%20tag%20on%20the%20supers