Evamor%2C%20Gentleman's%20Playbook%2C%20Glow%2C%20Keurig%2C%20and%20Oikos%2C%20according%20to%20ads%20he's%20appeared%20in%20or%20shared%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EForbes%20estimates%20that%20Prescott%20raked%20in%20a%20collective%20%2415%20million%20from%20his%20off-field%20ventures%20between%20May%202022%20and%20May%202023.%20He%20landed%20at%20No.%2046%20on%20the%20outlet's%202023%20list%20of%20the%20world's%20highest-paid%20athletes%20with%20a%20total%20estimated%20annual%20income%20of%20%2446%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20the%20official%20sum%20of%20money%20Prescott%20has%20to%20his%20name%20isn't%20available%20to%20the%20public%2C%20outlets%20including%20Yahoo%20Sports%20have%20cited%20%2460%20million%20as%20his%20net%20worth%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHe%20has%20used%20this%20money%20to%20make%20even%20more%20through%20shrewd%20investments.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222223%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dak%20Prescott.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6568d87658e7c0c29a2868ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDak%20Prescott.%3Cp%3ETim%20Heitman-USA%20TODAY%20Sports%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPrescott%20hasn't%20merely%20pocketed%20the%20millions%20upon%20millions%20he's%20made%20from%20his%20team%20and%20his%20sponsors%2C%20and%20not%20just%20because%20there's%20no%20way%20it'd%20fit.%20He's%20used%20his%20earnings%20to%20help%20grow%20his%20net%20worth%20by%20building%20an%20impressive%20investment%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dallas-based%20quarterback%20made%20a%20significant%20investment%20in%20a%20OxeFit%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0a%20fitness%20startup%20out%20of%20Plano%2C%20Texas%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0in%202021%20alongside%20several%20other%20NFL%20stars%2C%20according%20to%20Crunchbase.%20The%20brand%20combined%20robotics%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20create%20a%20workout%20machine%20that%20offers%20users%20coaching%20and%20feedback%20during%20strength%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20same%20year%2C%20Prescott%20purchased%20a%2020%25%20stake%20in%20sports%20bar%20and%20restaurant%20chain%20Walk-On's%2C%20per%20CNBC.%20Forbes%20reports%20that%20he%20is%20also%20part%20of%20the%20ownership%20groups%20of%20four%20individual%20franchises%20located%20in%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cowboys%20star%20bought%20into%20RealTruck%20%E2%80%94%20a%20manufacturer%20of%20accessories%20%E2%80%94%20in%202022%2C%20per%20Crunchbase.%20And%20in%20late%20November%202023%2C%20he%20invested%20in%20IMG%20Academy%2C%20a%20sports%20education%20company%20with%20a%20campus%20in%20Bradenton%2C%20Florida%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPrescott%20bought%20himself%20a%20sprawling%20estate%C2%A0less%20than%20an%20hour's%20drive%20from%20Dallas'%20home%20stadium.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20of%20Dak%20Prescott's%20home%20in%20Plano%2C%20Texas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6568eac386933e8fdb2e87e0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221248%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20aerial%20view%20of%20Dak%20Prescott's%20home%20in%20Plano%2C%20Texas.%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Earth%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Prescott%20dropped%20a%20cool%20%243.3%20million%20on%20a%20mansion%20in%20Prosper%2C%20Texas.%20According%20to%20Zillow%2C%20the%20five-bedroom%2C%20seven-bathroom%20home%20sits%20on%20seven%20acres%20of%20property%20that%20includes%20a%20private%20pond%2C%20a%20luxurious%20pool%20area%20with%20an%20attached%20spa%20and%20nearby%20fire%20pit%2C%20and%20plenty%20of%20patio%20space%20for%20entertaining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20the%20house%2C%20Prescott%20can%20enjoy%20a%20massive%20kitchen%20with%20granite%20countertops%20and%20stainless%20steel%20appliances%3B%20a%20game%20room%20complete%20with%20a%20sports%20simulator%20screen%2C%20pool%20table%2C%20bar%2C%20and%20jumbotron%20with%20four%20TVs%3B%20a%20movie%20theater%20with%20plush%20leather%20chairs%20and%20a%20massive%20projector%3B%20a%20huge%20main%20bedroom%20that%20boasts%20a%20fireplace%20and%20on-suite%20bathroom%20with%20a%20jetted%20tub%20and%20steam%20shower%3B%20a%20home%20gym%3B%20and%20an%20office%20with%20its%20own%20fireplace%20adjacent%20to%20the%20desk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20most%20unique%20aspect%20of%20the%20estate%20is%20the%20custom%20practice%20field%20Prescott%20built%20in%20his%20yard.%20ESPN%20reported%20that%20he%20hired%20the%20same%20company%20to%20install%20custom%20%26quot%3BDK4%26quot%3B%20logos%20and%20inscribe%20the%20word%20%26quot%3BFaith%26quot%3B%20across%20each%20end%20zone%20that%20the%20Cowboys%20employed%20to%20install%20the%20fields%20at%20AT%26amp%3BT%20Stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrescott%20later%20added%20a%20golf%20hole%20in%20the%20yard%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHe%20travels%20around%20Dallas%20in%20style%20thanks%20to%20his%20impressive%20collection%20of%20cars.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221874%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dak%20Prescott%20steps%20out%20of%20his%20Mercedes-Benz%20G63%20AMG.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6568ecd558e7c0c29a287504%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDak%20Prescott%20steps%20out%20of%20his%20Mercedes-Benz%20G63%20AMG.%3Cp%3EDak%20Prescott%2FInstagram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPrescott%20rarely%20rolls%20up%20to%20AT%26amp%3BT%20Stadium%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0or%20anywhere%20else%20nearby%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0in%20a%20car%20that's%20not%20fit%20for%20Cowboys%20royalty.%20According%20to%20Sportskeeda%2C%20he%20owns%20a%20Cadillac%20Escalade%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECorvette%20Stingray%2C%20Dodge%20Challenger%20SRT%20Hellcat%2C%20Lamborghini%20Urus%2C%20Mercedes-Benz%20C63%2C%20Mercedes-Benz%20G63%20AMG%2C%20and%20Tesla%20Model%20S.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhen%20he's%20not%2