20of%20the%20program%20and%20the%20length%20of%20time%20we%20often%20work%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Young%20colleagues%20discussing%20over%20computer%20at%20desk%20in%20office%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63c54ab6bcd21800196b7c53%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGen%20Z%20is%20making%20its%20mark%20on%20the%20workplace.%3Cp%3EMaskot%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20clients%20are%20from%20a%20variety%20of%20professional%20backgrounds.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20they%20all%20have%20in%20common%20is%20that%20when%20they%20finished%20their%20education%20they%20fell%20into%20a%20career%20influenced%20by%20what%20they%20thought%20looked%20good%20on%20paper%20or%20what%20their%20parents%20would%20approve%20of%20or%20perhaps%20they%20just%20took%20the%20first%20thing%20that%20was%20offered%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnywhere%20from%20two%20to%20five%20to%20seven%20years%20later%2C%20they%20come%20to%20me%20and%20say%3A%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20entirely%20sure%20how%20I%20ended%20up%20on%20this%20path.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20not%20sure%20what%20it%20is%20they%20want%20to%20do%20or%20how%20to%20step%20out%20of%20their%20current%20comfort%20zone.%20That%20can%20feel%20quite%20challenging.%20They%20often%20describe%20themselves%20as%20feeling%20quite%20lost%2C%20quite%20stuck%2C%20quite%20sad%2C%20and%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20whole%20heap%20of%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20work%20together%2C%20we%20follow%20a%20framework%20that%20helps%20them%20understand%20what%20they%20want%20and%20need%20from%20life%20and%20work%20and%20then%20create%20an%20action%20plan%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMillennials%20and%20Gen%20Z%20share%20some%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-versus-gen-z-wor