0addition%20to%20controlling%20resistance%20through%20your%20strokes%20%E2%80%94%20the%20harder%20and%20faster%20you%20row%2C%20the%20greater%20drag%20the%20flywheel%20encounters%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20increase%20resistance%20by%20adding%20water%20to%20the%20tank.%20In%20essence%2C%20the%20more%20water%20there%20is%2C%20the%20heavier%20the%20drag%20on%20the%20flywheel%2C%20and%20the%20harder%20your%20workout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaintenance%20of%20the%20machine%20is%20easy%2C%20too.%20Just%20fill%20the%20tank%20using%20the%20included%20siphon%20pump%20and%20drop%20in%20a%20chlorine%20tablet%20every%20six%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20comfortable%2C%20stable%20seat%20that%20rolls%20smoothly%20along%20dual%20rails%2C%20you'll%20experience%20an%20excellent%20workout%20where%20you%20can%20keep%20track%20of%20distance%2C%20time%2C%20and%20calories%20burned%20as%20displayed%20on%20the%20S4%20monitor.%20The%20rower%20comes%20with%20a%20three-year%20warranty%20on%20its%20parts%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20five-year%20warranty%20on%20the%20frame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20beginners%3A%20Sunny%20Health%20%26amp%3B%20Fitness%20Magnetic%20Rowing%20Machine%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221476%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20person%20uses%20the%20Sunny%20Health%20%26amp%3B%20Fitness%20Magnetic%20Rowing%20Machine%20against%20a%20white%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c65ea752628987dd355db92%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221107%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETension%20system%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Magnetic%20tension%20(8%20levels%20of%20resistance)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDimensions%20(length%20x%20width)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%206.5%20ft.%20x%201.6%20ft.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%20capacity%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E250%20lbs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDigital%20monitor%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20LCD%20monitor%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESmart%20features%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Time%2C%20distance%2C%20speed%2C%20and%20calorie%20count%20displayed%20by%20LCD%20screen%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMembership%20cost%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EN%2FA%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EEconomical%20with%20eight%20levels%20of%20resistance%2C%20easy%20to%20fold%20and%20store%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ENot%20the%20best%20cord%20quality%2C%20rail%20might%20be%20too%20short%20for%20tall%20people%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reasonably%20priced%20Sunny%20Health%20%26amp%3B%20Fitness%20Magnetic%20Rowing%20Machine%20offers%20quite%20a%20few%20convenient%20features%3A%20a%20comfortable%2C%20cushioned%20seat%3B%20anti-grip%20handles%3B%20an%20LCD%20monitor%20that%20tracks%20stroke%20counts%2C%20time%2C%20and%20calories%20burned%3B%20and%20eight%20levels%20of%20knob-adjusted%20magnetic%20resistance%20for%20various%20intensities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELevel%20two%20is%20good%20for%20warming%20up%20before%20progressing%20to%20levels%20three%20and%20four%20for%20a%20more%20vigorous%20workout.%20Levels%20five%20and%20higher%20are%20more%20intense%20and%20perfect%20for%20long%20cardio-building%20rowing%20sessions.%20Level%20seven%20is%20for%20endurance%20and%20all-out%20sprints%20while%20level%20eight%20offers%20the%20greatest%20resistance%20(and%20hardest%20workout).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAble%20to%20support%20up%20to%20250%20pounds%2C%20Sunny's%20Magnetic%20Rowing%20Machine%20has%20a%2048-inch-long%20rail%20in%20which%20the%20padded%20seat%20rolls%20smoothly%20and%20quietly.%20The%20rower%20is%20able%20to%20easily%20fold%20up%20for%20convenient%20storage%20and%20even%20has%20built-in%20wheels.%20It's%20easy%20to%20assemble%20and%20relatively%20compact%2C%20taking%20up%20minimal%20space%20when%20folded%20up%20and%20very%20little%20square%20footage%20when%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20I%20test%20rowing%20machines%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22person%20sitting%20on%20an%20ergatta%20rowing%20machine%20in%20a%20living%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6299137d3efa8c0019aaaac8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERick%20Stella%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20rower%20featured%20in%20this%20guide%20went%20through%20a%20testing%20process%20to%20gauge%20how%20well%20it%20performed%20across%20these%20four%20categories%3A%20%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%2C%20experience%2C%20reliability%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3Evalue.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Here's%20how%20each%20category%20specifically%20factored%20into%20which%20rowers%20ultimately%20made%20this%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ERow%20machines%20have%20a%20naturally%20low%20learning%20curve%20%E2%80%94%20the%20general%20idea%20is%20to%20just%20sit%20down%20and%20row.%20But%20we%20know%20there's%20more%20to%20it%20than%20that.%20Ease%20of%20use%20also%20refers%20to%20the%20process%20of%20setting%20up%20the%20machine%20set%20up%20in%20your%20home%2C%20how%20easy%20it%20is%20to%20get%20started%2C%20whether%20there's%20a%20companion%20app%2C%20and%20if%20that%20learning%20curve%20(however%20steep)%20dramatically%20impacts%20the%20following%20category%3A%20your%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExperience%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EWorking%20out%20for%20fun%20may%20seem%20like%20an%20oxymoron%20but%20it%20is%20important%20to%20at%20least%20somewhat%20enjoy%20the%20sweat%20your%20breaking.%20Since%20a%20row%20machine%20delivers%20a%20full-body%20workout%2C%20you%20want%20one%20that%20won't%20feel%20like%20some%20sort%20of%20grueling%20game%20of%20tug%20of%20war.%20Ideally%2C%20a%20proper%20row%20machine%20offers%20smooth%20operation%2C%20an%20engaging%20platform%20(whether%20that%20means%20it%20offers%20digital%20feedback%20or%20is%20just%20fluid%20to%20use)%2C%20and%20is%20comfortable%20to%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReliability%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20the%20rowing%20machine%20you%20invest%20in%20doesn't%20last%20longer%20than%20a%20few%20months%2C%20you'll%20likely%20be%20cursing%20whatever%20inclination%20you%20had%20to%20want%20to%20buy%20it.%20Put%20plainly%2C%20at-home%20workout%20machines%20aren't%20cheap%20and%20the%20one%20you%20ultimately%20end%20up%20spending%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20money%20on%20should%20work%20and%20work%20often.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EValue%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EValue%20is%20a%20mixture%20of%20the%20categories%20that%20came%20before%20it%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20attention%20to%20its%20actual%20sticker%20price%20%E2%80%94%20but%20this%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20more%20expensive%20models%20should%20be%20ignored.%20It's%20better%20to%20spend%20more%20money%20once%20on%20a%20machine%20that's%20reliable%2C%20easy%20to%20use%2C%20and%20delivers%20a%20fun%20workout%20than%20to%20struggle%20with%20a%20different%20cumbersome%20budget%20model%20every%20few%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20to%20correctly%20use%20a%20rowing%20machine%3Cp%3EProper%20rowing%20form%20consists%20of%20an%20initial%20drive%20phase%20followed%20by%20a%20recovery%20phase%2C%20and%20it's%20the%20best%20way%20to%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20your%20workouts%20and%20avoid%20injury.%20Here's%20how%20to%20execute%20it%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20%3Cstrong%3Edrive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20start%20first%20with%20your%20legs%20and%20once%20those%20are%20extended%20and%20your%20back%20is%20vertical%2C%20use%20your%20arms%20to%20pull%20the%20handle%20into%20your%20body.%20Your%20finished%20position%20should%20be%20your%20legs%20fully%20extended%2C%20the%20rower's%20handle%20pulled%20into%20your%20body%20with%20your%20wrists%20in%20line%20with%20your%20forearms.%20From%20here%2C%20you'll%20move%20on%20to%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20step%20of%20%3Cstrong%3Erecovery%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20to%20straighten%20your%20arms%20and%20pivot%20your%20body%20from%20your%20hips%2C%20making%20sure%20to%20avoid%20hunching%20forward%20or%20bending%20backward.%20This%20fluid%20motion%20will%20then%20have%20your%20legs%20flexing%20in%20until%20your%20shins%20are%20completely%20vertical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20don't%20think%20of%20this%20exercise%20as%20a%20race.%20Focus%20on%20perfecting%20your%20form%2C%20not%20on%20how%20fast%20you%20can%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERowing%20Machine%20FAQs%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20rowing%20better%20than%20running%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ERowing%20activates%20more%20muscle%20groups%20than%20just%20running%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctor-says-rowing-on-a-machine-more-effective-than-running-on-treadmill-2018-3%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20study%20by%20Dr.%20Cameron%20Nichol%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20former%20Olympic%20rower.%20In%20addition%20to%20activating%20roughly%2085%25%20of%20your%20body's%20muscles%20and%20upwards%20of%20nine%20different%20muscle%20groups%2C%20rowing%20also%20helps%20strengthen%20your%20back%2C%20tone%20your%20arms%2C%20and%20benefit%20both%20your%20upper%20and%20lower%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20row%20every%20day%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20yes.%20But%20like%20any%20workout%20routine%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20not%20overdo%20it%20or%20consistently%20push%20yourself%20over%20your%20limit.%20Personal%20trainer%2C%20Irving%20Hyppolite%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftrainer-diet-tips-for-will-smith-dad-bod-fitness-2021-5%5C%22%3Etold%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20people%20tend%20to%20try%20to%20do%20too%20much%20and%20that%20there's%20an%20actual%20limit%20on%20how%20much%20your%20body%20can%20handle.%20Hyppolite%20says%20three%20to%20five%20days%20a%20week%20of%20exercising%20from%2045%20minutes%20to%20an%20hour%20(including%20warm-up%20and%20cooldown)%20is%20a%20good%20standard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20lose%20weight%20by%20using%20a%20rowing%20machine%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EConsistent%20exercise%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-get-fit-workouts-summer-diet-training-advice-personal-trainers-2021-3%5C%22%3Ejust%20one%20component%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20being%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fweight-loss-tips%5C%22%3Emanage%20your%20weight%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20it's%20irresponsible%20to%20say%20that%20a%20rower%20can%20be%20singularly%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fhow-to-lose-weight-and-keep-it-off%5C%22%3Ehelp%20you%20lose%20weight%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Caley%20Crawford%2C%20NASM%20CPT%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.therowhouse.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDirector%20of%20Education%20for%20Row%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bit's%20crucial%20that%20you%20partner%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwhat-is-dash-diet%5C%22%3Estrong%20and%20healthy%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20your%20exercise%20routine.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20type%20of%20rowing%20machine%20is%20best%20for%20home%20use%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20rowing%20machine%20for%20home%20use%20depends%20on%20the%20amount%20of%20space%20you%20have%20to%20use%20a%20machine%20as%20big%20as%20a%20rower.%20Some%20rowers%20do%20fold%20up%2C%20making%20them%20easier%20to%20store%20against%20a%20wall%20or%20even%20stash%20in%20a%20garage%2C%20but%20many%20others%20do%20not%20and%20will%20take%20up%20a%20large%20footprint.%20Measure%20the%20amount%20of%20available%20space%20you%20have%20in%20your%20home%20and%20compare%20the%20sizes%20of%20each%20rower%20you're%20considering%20to%20get%20an%20idea%20of%20what%20fits%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20build%20muscle%20with%20a%20rowing%20machine%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20using%20a%20rowing%20machine%20is%20a%20great%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-to-use-gym-machines-to-build-muscle-for-beginners-2022-10%23the-rower-can-build-muscle-and-give-you-a-cardio-workout-at-the-same-time-7%5C%22%3Ebeginner-friendly%20way%20to%20build%20muscle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Plus%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ffitness%2Frowing-machine-benefits%5C%22%3Eworks%20your%20entire%20body%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20allowing%20you%20to%20strengthen%20a%20variety%20of%20muscles%20and%20it's%20a%20much%20more%20low-impact%20workout%20than%20something%20like%20running%20or%20lifting%20weights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20consider%20when%20buying%20a%20rowing%20machine%3Cp%3EWith%20so%20many%20different%20kinds%20of%20rowers%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20examine%20each%20model%20to%20choose%20one%20that%20best%20fits%20your%20needs%20and%20keeps%20you%20motivated%20and%20injury-free.%20You'll%20want%20to%20consider%20features%20like%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EType%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAt-home%20rowers%20are%20available%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20types%2C%20including%20folding%20options%2C%20those%20that%20come%20with%20a%20water%20reservoir%2C%20and%20others%20that%20have%20independently%20moving%20handles.%20There%20are%20also%20a%20number%20of%20resistance%20types%20(more%20below)%20that%20differentiate%20rowers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EResistance%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Different%20types%20of%20resistance%20include%20magnetic%20(electromagnets%20slow%20the%20erg's%20metal%20flywheel)%2C%20air%20(wind%20from%20the%20spinning%20flywheel%20creates%20drag)%2C%20hydraulic%20(resistance%20is%20created%20by%20hydraulic%20fluid%20in%20a%20piston%20or%20two%20connected%20to%20the%20erg's%20handles)%2C%20and%20water%20(the%20flywheel%20pushes%20against%20water%20in%20a%20tank).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrice%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPrice%20for%20rowers%20can%20cost%20anywhere%20from%20%24150%20for%20a%20basic%2C%20entry-level%20option%20on%20up%20to%20%242%2C000%2B%20for%20a%20smart%20rower%20that%20comes%20with%20a%20built-in%20screen%20and%20that%20offers%20streamable%20workouts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaintenance%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMost%20rowers%20need%20to%20simply%20be%20wiped%20down%20after%20it's%20used%20to%20preserve%20its%20durability.%20This%20includes%20wiping%20off%20any%20sweat%20and%20cleaning%20any%20grime%20that%20appears.%20Rowers%20that%20feature%20a%20water%20reservoir%20also%20need%20to%20have%20their%20water%20treated%20occasionally%20and%20it's%20also%20smart%20to%20clean%20out%20the%20reservoir%20every%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaximum%20user%20weight%20capacity%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Models%20vary%20in%20how%20much%20they%20support%20but%20many%20accommodate%20220%20to%20265%20pounds%20or%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20machine%20should%20be%20large%20enough%20for%20you%20to%20straighten%20your%20legs%20and%20maintain%20proper%20rowing%20form%2C%20yet%20small%20enough%20to%20fit%20into%20your%20workout%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFoldability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Some%20machines%20(usually%20magnetic%20and%20hydraulic%20resistance)%20fold%20up%20for%20easy%20storage%2C%20while%20others%20(often%20air%20and%20water%20resistance)%20don't.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMonitor%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20monitor%20or%20computer%20tracks%20information%20like%20distance%2C%20duration%2C%20speed%2C%20and%2For%20calories%20burned%20while%20rowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeat%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20should%20be%20contoured%20and%20large%20enough%20to%20keep%20your%20backside%20comfortable%20while%20allowing%20you%20to%20maintain%20proper%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20a