is%20job%2C%20his%20counterpart%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20might%20just%20lose%20his%2C%20they%20indicate.%20There%20also%20seems%20a%20high%20possibility%20that%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20could%C2%A0%20go%20to%20the%20BJP%20--%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20upset%2C%20though%2C%20could%20be%20reserved%20for%20Telangana%2C%20where%20K%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao's%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20has%20been%20in%20power%20since%20the%20inception%20of%20the%20state%20in%202014.%20NDTV%20Poll%20of%20Polls%20--%20an%20aggregate%20of%20seven%20exit%20polls%20--%20shows%20the%20Congress%20ahead%20in%2062%20of%20the%20state's%20119%20seats%2C%20the%20BRS%20on%C2%A0%2044.%20The%20BJP%20can%20win%20seven%20seats%20and%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi's%20AIMIM%20five%20seats.%20The%20majority%20mark%20stands%20at%2060.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Mizoram%2C%20an%20aggregate%20of%20six%20exit%20polls%20indicate%20a%20hung%20house.%20Two%20exit%20polls%20predict%20the%20BJP-MNF's%20ruling%20alliance%20have%20a%20slim%20chance%20of%20victory.%20Only%20one%20predict%20a%20sweep%20for%20the%20new%20party%20Zoram%20People's%20Movement%20(ZPM).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExit%20polls%2C%20though%2C%20can%20often%20get%20it%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.ndtv.com%2Fe%2Fassembly%2F2023%2Fdecember%2Fexitpoll%2Fpollofpoll.html%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22description%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22340px%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20aggregate%20of%20nine%20exit%20polls%20on%20Chhattisgarh%20predict%20a%20second%20term%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20has%20been%20banking%20on%20Bhupesh%20Baghel's%20report%20card%20for%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20The%20number%20of%20seats%20allotted%20to%20the%20party%20has%20been%20within%20the%20margin%20of%20early%2040s%20to%20mid-50s.%20The%20majority%20mark%20in%20the%2090-seat%20state%20stands%20at%2046.%20NDTV%20Poll%20of%20Polls%20indicates%20that%2049%20seats%20can%20go%20to%20the%20Congress%20and%2038%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.ndtv.com%2Fe%2Fassembly%2F2023%2Fdecember%2Fexitpoll%2Fexitpoll_embed.html%3Fstatenm%3DCHH%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22description%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22340px%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeighbouring%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20though%2C%20could%20have%20bad%20news%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20unseat%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan.%20The%20BJP's%20three-time%20Chief%20Minister%20came%20to%20power%20yet%20again%20in%202020%20despite%20a%20defeat%20in%202018%2C%20with%20the%20crossing%20over%20of%20Congress's%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20and%20his%2020-plus%20loyalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20aggregate%20of%20nine%20exit%20polls%20indicates%20that%20the%20BJP%20may%20wind%20up%20with%20124%20of%20the%20state's%20230%20seats%2C%20where%20the%20majority%20mark%20is%20116.%20The%20Congress%20may%20get%20102%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20definitive%20verdict%20is%20from%20News%2024-Today's%20Chanakya%2C%20which%20gives%20BJP%20151%20seats%2C%20and%20the%20Congress%2074.%20Others%20predict%20a%20tight%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20was%2C%20held%20amid%20much%20speculation%20of%20anti-incumbency%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20largely%20ruled%20the%20state%20since%202004.%20With%20four%20terms%20under%20his%20belt%2C%20Mr%20Chouhan%20is%20one%20of%20the%20BJP's%20longest-ruling%20Chief%20Ministers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.ndtv.com%2Fe%2Fassembly%2F2023%2Fdecember%2Fexitpoll%2Fexitpoll_embed.html%3Fstatenm%3DMP%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22description%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22340px%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajasthan%2C%20which%20routinely%20votes%20out%20the%20incumbent%20since%20early%20'90s%2C%20is%20apparently%20sticking%20to%20the%20custom%2C%20overturning%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot's%20high%20hope%20of%20bucking%20the%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeven%20of%20nine%20exit%20polls%20have%20predicted%20a%20comfortable%20victory%20for%20the%20BJP%20--%20only%20two%20offer%20Congress%20the%20hope%20that%20it%20might%20scrape%20through.%20Most%20exit%20polls%20expect%20the%20BJP%20numbers%20to%20stay%20above%20100%20in%20the%20200-member%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20election%20had%C2%A0%20taken%20place%20on%20199%20seats%20following%20the%20death%20of%20a%20Congress%20candidate%2C%20the%20majority%20mark%20will%20be%20101.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20Poll%20of%20Polls%20indicates%20that%20the%20BJP%20can%20get%20104%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%2085.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.ndtv.com%2Fe%2Fassembly%2F2023%2Fdecember%2Fexitpoll%2Fexitpoll_embed.html%3Fstatenm%3DRAJ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22description%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22340px%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2040-seat%20Mizoram%2C%20only%20two%20of%20six%20exit%20polls%20predict%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20ally%2C%20the%20Mizo%20National%20Front%2C%20might%20make%20it%20to%20the%20seat%20of%20power%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aggregate%20of%20six%20exit%20polls%20indicates%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20can%20get%2015%20seats%2C%20the%20new%20Zoram%20People's%20Movement%20(ZPM)%2017%2C%20which%20could%20put%20Congress%2C%20expected%20to%20win%20seven%20seats%2C%20in%20the%20position%20of%20the%20kingmaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chances%20of%20hung%20house%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state%20run%20high%2C%20with%20a%20multi-cornered%20contest%20that%20included%20the%20rising%20ZPM%2C%20which%20projected%20a%20young%20face%20for%20the%20state's%20top%20job.%20All%20exit%20polls%20have%20given%20the%20new%20party%20a%20chunk%20of%20seats%2C%20pushing%20the%20Congress%20to%20the%20third%20spot%20in%20the%20s