sely%2C%20they%20have%20attempted%20to%20dilute%20their%20financial%20obligations%20and%20resisted%20defining%20a%20clear%20finance%20mobilisation%20scale%E2%80%A6The%20absence%20of%20a%20defined%20replenishment%20cycle%20raises%20serious%20questions%20about%20the%20Fund%E2%80%99s%20long-term%20sustainability.%20Therefore%2C%20a%20robust%20system%2C%20particularly%20integrated%20with%20the%20Global%20Stocktake%20process%20and%20the%20new%20climate%20finance%20goal%2C%20is%20needed%20to%20ensure%20that%20COP28%20results%20in%20a%20meaningful%20outcome.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAffluent%20nations%20must%20meet%20their%20financial%20obligations%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmanner%20proportionate%20to%20their%20role%20in%20the%20climate%20crisis%2C%20which%20has%20been%20primarily%20driven%20by%20decades%20of%20unrestrained%20fossil%20fuel%20consumption%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20adequate%20climate%20finance%20delivered%20to%20the%20Global%20South%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ELast%20nine%20years%20have%20been%20the%20warmest%20ever%3A%20WMO%20report%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20World%20Meteorological%20Organisation%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwmo.int%2Fnews%2Fmedia-centre%2F2023-shatters-climate-records-major-impacts%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eprovisional%20State%20of%20the%20Global%20Climate%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20published%20on%20November%2030%20to%20inform%20negotiations%20at%20COP28%20in%20Dubai%2C%20confirmed%20that%202023%20is%20set%20to%20be%20the%20warmest%20year%20on%20record.%20Data%20until%20the%20end%20of%20October%20shows%20that%20the%20year%20was%20about%201.4%20Degrees%20Celsius%20above%20the%20pre-industrial%201850-1900%20baseline%2C%20it%20said.%20The%20past%20nine%20years%20%E2%80%93%202015%20to%202023%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20the%20warmest%20ever.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CGreenhouse%20gas%20levels%20are%20record%20high.%20Global%20temperatures%20are%20record%20high.%20Sea%20level%20rise%20is%20record%20high.%20Antarctic%20sea%20ice%20is%20record%20low.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20deafening%20cacophony%20of%20broken%20records%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20WMO%20Secretary-General%20Prof.%20Petteri%20Taalas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%202023%20WMO%20report%20rings%20a%20dire%20warning%20for%20India%2C%20underlining%20the%20stark%20reality%20of%20a%20planet%20in%20crisis%2C%20said%20Anjal%20Prakash%2C%20Clinical%20Associate%20Professor%20(Research)%20and%20Research%20Director%2C%20Bharti%20Institute%20of%20Public%20Policy%2C%20Indian%20School%20of%20Business%20and%20an%20IPCC%20author.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUnprecedented%20heatwaves%2C%20soaring%20greenhouse%20gas%20levels%2C%20and%20alarming%20declines%20in%20Antarctic%20Sea%20ice%20demand%20urgent%20attention%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20faces%20severe%20repercussions%20as%20rising%20temperatures%20exacerbate%20heatwaves%2C%20impacting%20agriculture%2C%20water%20resources%2C%20and%20public%20health.%20The%20heightened%20risk%20of%20extreme%20weather%20events%2C%20floods%2C%20and%20cyclones%20poses%20a%20direct%20threat%20to%20vulnerable%20communities.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20we%20approach%20COP28%2C%20India%20stands%20at%20a%20crossroads%20where%20immediate%20and%20decisive%20actions%2C%20including%20ramping%20up%20renewable%20energy%2C%20are%20imperative%20to%20safeguard%20our%20nation%E2%80%99s%20future%2C%20he%20added.%20%E2%80%9CThe%201.5-degree%20limit%20remains%20achievable%2C%20provided%20leaders%20prioritise%20sustainable%20policies%20over%20short-term%20gains.%20Let%20this%20report%20serve%20as%20a%20call%20to%20action%20for%20India%20and%20the%20world%2C%20recognising%20that%20the%20choices%20we%20make%20today%20will%20determine%20the%20well-being%20of%20generations%20to%20come.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIndia%20and%20COP28%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20inaugurated%20its%20COP28%20pavilion%20on%20November%2030.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20keeping%20with%20our%20civilisational%20ethos%2C%20India%20has%20always%20laid%20emphasis%20on%20climate%20action%20even%20as%20we%20pursue%20social%20and%20economic%20development%2C%E2%80%9D%20India%E2%80%99s%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1981197%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20November%2030%2C%20just%20before%20setting%20off%20to%20attend%20COP28.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ELeaving%20for%20Dubai%2C%20where%20I%20will%20take%20part%20in%20the%20COP-28%20Summit.%20This%20forum%20will%20witness%20important%20deliberations%20to%20strengthen%20the%20efforts%20to%20overcome%20climate%20change%20and%20further%20sustainable%20development.%20I%20will%20also%20be%20interacting%20with%20various%20world%20leaders%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1730222162588631463%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2030%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20our%20G20%20Presidency%2C%20climate%20was%20high%20on%20our%20priority%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20the%20press%20release.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20New%20Delhi%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Declaration%20includes%20numerous%20concrete%20steps%20on%20climate%20action%20and%20sustainable%20development.%20I%20look%20forward%20to%20the%20COP-28%20taking%20forward%20the%20consensus%20on%20these%20issues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20leaders%20at%20the%20G20%20summit%20%E2%80%93%20which%20India%20hosted%20in%20September%20this%20year%20%E2%80%93%20failed%20to%20reach%20a%20consensus%20on%20several%20aspects%20of%20climate%20action.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECOP28%20will%20also%20provide%20an%20opportunity%20to%20review%20progress%20made%20under%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%2C%20and%20chart%20a%20path%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfuture%20course%20on%20climate%20action%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20PM%20said%20in%20his%20release.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20Voice%20of%20Global%20South%20Summit%20convened%20by%20India%2C%20the%20Global%20South%20spoke%20for%20the%20need%20for%20climate%20action%20based%20on%20the%20principles%20of%20equity%2C%20climate%20justice%2C%20and%20common%20but%20differentiated%20responsibilities%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20greater%20focus%20on%20adaptation.%20It%20is%20important%20that%20efforts%20of%20the%20developing%20world%20be%20supported%20with%20adequate%20climate%20financing%20and%20technology%20transfer.%20They%20must%20have%20access%20to%20equitable%20carbon%20and%20development%20space%20to%20achieve%20sustainable%20development.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20year%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20COPs%2C%20health%20is%20on%20the%20agenda.%20An%20entire%20day%20%E2%80%93%20December%203%20%E2%80%93%20will%20be%20dedicated%20to%20discussions%20on%20health%20alone.%20However%2C%20while%2070%20countries%20are%20sending%20their%20ministers%2C%20there%20is%20no%20official%20communication%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20yet%20on%20whether%20India%E2%80%99s%20representatives%20will%20be%20at%20this%20crucial%20meeting%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fnov%2F29%2Fcop28-india-not-sending-delegation-to-crucial-climate-health-meet-in-dubai-on-december-3-2637279.html%3Futm_source%3Dsubstack%26utm_medium%3Demail%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20t%3Cspan%3Ehe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20expects%20a%20%E2%80%9Cclear%20roadmap%E2%80%9D%20on%20climate%20finance%20at%20the%20ongoing%20COP28%20in%20Dubai%2C%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Vinay%20Kwatra%20said%20on%20November%2030%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Findia-expects-clear-roadmap-on-climate-finance-during-cop28-foreign-secretary-kwatra%2F1865755%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECOP28%3A%20Already%20mired%20in%20controversy%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2028th%20annual%20climate%20change%20conference%2C%20however%2C%20is%20already%20mired%20in%20controversy%2C%20as%20reports%20reveal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20the%20appointment%20of%20Sultan%20Ahmed%20Al-Jaber%20as%20the%20president-designate%20of%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20COP%20raised%20heavy%20criticism.%20Al%20Jaber%20is%20UAE%E2%80%99s%20Minister%20of%20Industry%20and%20Advanced%20Technology%2C%20as%20well%20as%20CEO%20of%20ADNOC%2C%20the%20Abu%20Dhabi%20National%20Oil%20Company.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fharjeet11%2Fstatus%2F1613482020583378945%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EActivists%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20called%20the%20move%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20problematic%E2%80%9D%20and%20have%20criticised%20the%20appointment%20saying%20it%20is%20in%20direct%20conflict%20of%20interest%20to%20the%20COP%2C%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fuae-oil-company-adnoc-ceo-cop28-president%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20January%20this%20year.%20Incidentally%2C%20on%20January%201%2C%20ADNOC%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spglobal.com%2Fcommodityinsights%2Fen%2Fmarket-insights%2Flatest-news%2Fnatural-gas%2F011023-uaes-adnoc-forms-new-gas-company-as-it-seeks-to-expand-internationally%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eformed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20a%20new%20gas%20company%20by%20merging%20its%20gas%20and%20LNG%20joint%20ventures%20with%20international%20oil%20companies%20to%20expand%20its%20international%20presence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20recently%2C%20leaked%20documents%20revealed%20that%20the%20UAE%20planned%20to%20use%20its%20role%20as%20the%20host%20of%20UN%20climate%20talks%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20strike%20oil%20and%20gas%20deals%20with%2015%20nations%2C%20the%20BBC%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-67508331%3Futm_source%3Dsubstack%26utm_medium%3Demail%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20In%20their%20report%20published%20three%20days%20ago%2C%20it%20said%20that%20the%20documents%20revealed%20that%20ADNOC%20is%20willing%20to%20work%20with%20these%20governments%2C%20including%20Colombia%2C%20to%20develop%20fossil%20fuel%20projects%20in%20these%20countries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAl-Jaber%2C%20however%2C%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fenvironment%2F2023%2Fnov%2F29%2Fcop28-president-denies-on-eve-of-summit-he-abused-his-position-to-sign-oil-deals%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erefuted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20allegations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECalling%20the%20allegations%20%E2%80%9Cfalse%2C%20not%20true%2C%20incorrect%20and%20not%20accurate%E2%80%9D%20at%20a%20media%20briefing%20on%20November%2029%2C%20Al-Jaber%20said%20that%20the%20UAE%20did%20not%20need%20the%20COP%20or%20the%20COP%20presidency%20to%20establish%20commercial%20oil%20deals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701366396000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-co