%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20that%20I%20doubt%20Shubman's%20skill%20or%20ability%20as%20a%20leader%20but%20the%20minute%20I%20saw%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kane%20Williamson%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1058-kane-williamson-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKane%20Williamson%3C%2Fa%3E's%20name%20as%20a%20retained%20player%20(in%20GT)%2C%20I%20thought%20there%20was%20a%20fantastic%20opportunity%20to%20give%20an%20experienced%20player%20who%20has%20done%20it%20before%2C%20player%20with%20a%20rock-solid%20role%20up%20the%20order%2C%20an%20opportunity%20to%20captain%20for%20you.%20Give%20Shubman%20Gill%20the%20opportunity%2C%20just%20to%20cement%20himself%20in%20all%20the%20formats%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20and%20just%20to%20have%20another%20good%20season%20at%20the%20IPL%2C%26quot%3B%20De%20Villiers%20said%20on%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSCVGX2l6p8g%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20no%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20throw%20him%20in%20as%20captain.%20It%20may%20pay%20off%3B%20I%20am%20not%20saying%20it%20is%20wrong.%20I%20am%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20a%20great%20opportunity%20for%20Shubman%20just%20to%20learn%20a%20little%20bit%20and%20know%20that%20the%20plan%20is%20for%20him%20to%20be%20captain%20in%202025.%20Nonetheless%2C%20I%20am%20excited%20to%20watch%20him%20perform%20and%20lead%20from%20the%20front.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20Gill's%20maiden%20outing%20as%20captain%20of%20an%20IPL%20side%2C%20having%20begun%20his%20journey%20in%20the%20competition%20in%202018%20with%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20before%20heading%20to%20GT%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20know%20captainship%20comes%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20things%2C%20and%20commitment%20is%20one%20of%20them.%20Discipline%20is%20one%20of%20them.%20Hard%20work%20is%20one%20of%20them.%20Loyalty%20is%20one%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gill%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20by%20the%20franchise%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%2C%20because%2C%20I%20think%20I've%20played%20under%20great%20leaders%20and%20I've%20learned%20a%20lot%20from%20them%2C%20I%20think%20those%20learnings%20that%20I%20have%20had%20from%20their%20experience%20playing%20under%20them%20is%20gonna%20help%20me%20a%20lot%20in%20this%20IPL.%26quot%3B%20Gill%20added%20that%20there%20was%20no%20dearth%20of%20experienced%20players%20in%20Gujarat%20Titans%2C%20and%20he%20would%20get%20to%20learn%20a%20lot%20from%20leaders%20such%20as%20New%20Zealand's%20Kane%20Williamson%20and%20Afghanistan's%20Rashid%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20great%20leaders%20in%20our%20team%2C%20be%20it%20Kane%20(Williamson)%20or%20be%20it%20Rashid%20(Khan)%20or%20be%20it%20(Mohammed)%20Shami%2C%20or%20even%20David%20(Miller)%2C%20or%20even%20Wriddhi%20(Saha).%20So%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20gonna%20be%20great.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20obviously%2C%20there%20are%20gonna%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20learnings%20along%20the%20way%2C%20which%20would%20be%20my%20experience%20as%20a%20captain.%20And%20I%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20making%20great%20memories%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20playing%20the%20leadership%20role%20is%20concerned%2C%20Gill%20was%20the%20India%20U-19%20vice-captain%20during%20the%202018%20World%20Cup.%20He%20was%20also%20named%20skipper%20of%20India%20Blue%20during%20the%202019-20%20Duleep%20Trophy%2C%20the%20India%20C%20captain%20in%20the%20Deodhar%20Trophy%20the%20same%20season%2C%20and%20the%20India-A%20leader%20during%20the%20New%20Zealand%20tour%20later%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701361860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Frkhs1h88_shubman-gill-and-hardik-pandya_625x300_27_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fnot-shubman-gill-rcb-great-feels-this-veteran-should-have