t%20worker%20emerged%20moments%20later.%20Within%20an%20hour%2C%20all%2041%20had%20been%20evacuated.%20The%20nation%20cheered%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20moment%20was%2C%20perhaps%2C%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20popular%20psyche%2C%20the%20biggest%20manifestation%20of%20New%20India%20in%20the%20making.%20A%20self-confident%20nation%2C%20which%20cared%20for%20its%20people%2C%20which%20would%20do%20anything%20and%20everything%2C%20even%20move%20a%20mighty%20mountain%20to%20keep%20its%20people%20alive%20and%20kicking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20catch-phrase%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BImpossible%20is%20nothing%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20a%20popular%20sports%20brand%20ad%20came%20to%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20unfolded%20in%20the%20two-week%20rescue%20mission%20belied%20that%20widely%20quoted%20adage%20-%20%26quot%3Btoo%20many%20cooks%20spoil%20the%20broth%26quot%3B.%20About%201%2C000%20people%20from%20a%20dozen%20agencies%20-%20NDRF%20(National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force)%2C%20SDRF%20(State%20Disaster%20Response%20Force)%2C%20BRO%20(Border%20Roads%20Organisation)%2C%20ONGC%2C%20National%20Highways%20and%20Infrastructure%20Corporation%2C%20Tehri%20Hydro%20Development%20Corporation%2C%20Satlaj%20Vidyut%20Nigam%2C%20Rail%20Vikas%20Nigam%2C%20Trenchless%20Engineering%2C%20Indian%20Army%2C%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20-%20worked%20in%20tandem%20for%2017%20days.%20Chief%20Minister%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami%20and%20a%20central%20minister%2C%20Gen%20(Retd)%20VK%20Singh%2C%20along%20with%20senior%20officials%20were%20stationed%20at%20the%20spot%20for%20days.%20Some%20leading%20experts%20were%20flown%20in%20from%20abroad%2C%20top%20officials%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20Office%20were%20constantly%20on%20the%20job.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20monitored%20the%20operation%20daily%20and%20issued%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMen%20and%20machines%20were%20flown%20in%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20There%20never%20was%20any%20confusion%2C%20no%20inter-agencies%20conflict.%20There%20was%20coordination%20and%20cooperation%2C%20something%20so%20far%20unheard%20of.%20It%20underlined%20that%20strong%20political%20will%20and%20concern%20for%20the%20people%20can%20make%20a%20big%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20may%20note%20that%20in%20this%20year's%20Independence%20Day%20speech%20PM%20Modi%20had%20talked%20eloquently%20about%20the%20contribution%20made%20by%20the%3Cem%3E%20Vishkarmas%2C%20Shramjivis%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20workers%20in%20nation%20building.%20He%20had%20recently%20announced%20a%20special%20scheme%20for%20them.%20Forty-one%20such%20%3Cem%3EShramjivis%2FVishwakarmas%3C%2Fem%3E%20trapped%20in%20the%20tunnel%20presented%20a%20giant%20challenge%20for%20rescuers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20close%20to%20a%20decade%2C%20a%20rising%20India%20has%20is%20built%20a%20new%20persona%20for%20itself%2C%20for%20within%20the%20nation%20and%20outside.%20%3Cem%3EAtmanirbhar%20Bharat%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20no%20hollow%20slogan.%20It%20is%20manifested%20in%20different%20sectors%20relating%20to%20security%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20innovation%2C%20economy%20and%20welfare%20of%20its%20people%20through%20fair%20and%20transparent%20last%20mile%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20seeker%20India%20has%20become%20a%20giver%20to%20the%20world.%20In%20nine%20and%20half%20years%20of%20the%20Modi%20regime%2C%20it%20has%20built%20a%20reputation%20of%20first%20responder%20in%20a%20crisis%20situation%20-%20be%20it%20by%20offering%20help%20to%20the%20Global%20South%20during%20Covid%2C%20or%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20devastating%20earthquake%20in%20Nepal%2C%20or%20more%20recently%20in%20Syria%20and%20Turkey%2C%20or%20in%20aftermath%20of%20a%20political%20crisis%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20or%20calling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20would%20leave%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20evacuate%20its%20people%2C%20howsoever%20big%20or%20small%20numbers%20that%20may%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Months%20after%20Modi%20came%20to%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%20in%202014%2C%20India%20safely%20evacuated%20Christian%20priest%20Father%20Alexis%20Prem%20Kumar%2C%20who%20had%20been%20kidnapped%20in%20Afghanistan%20eight%20months%20previously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20The%20latest%20was%20Operation%20Ajay%2C%20when%20India%20evacuated%20Indians%20from%20Israel%20and%20Gaza%20amidst%20the%20most%20lethal%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Operation%20Kaveri%20was%20launched%20to%20evacuate%20around%202%2C500%20Indians%20stranded%20in%20Sudan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Operation%20Ganga%20was%20launched%20in%202022%20to%20evacuate%20Indian%20nationals%20stranded%20in%20Ukraine%20when%20its%20war%20against%20Russia%20erupted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Operation%20Devi%20Shakti%20was%20launched%20in%202021%20to%20bring%20back%20Indian%20from%20Afghanistan%20after%20the%20Americans%20left%20Kabul%20and%20Taliban%20took%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Operation%20Samudra%20Setu%2C%20a%20naval%20operation%2C%20was%20launched%20in%202020%20after%20Covid%20broke%20out%20to%20bring%20back%20Indian%20citizens%20from%20overseas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Through%20operation%20Vande%20Bharat%202020%2C%20lakhs%20of%20Indians%20were%20brought%20back%20from%20foreign%20countries%20amid%20Covid%20lockdowns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Operation%20Nistar%20in%202018%20was%20initiated%20after%20a%20severe%20cyclonic%20storm%20wreaked%20havoc%20around%20Socotra%20Island%20in%20Yemen.%20Indian%20Navy%20evacuated%2038%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20In%202016%20around%20250%20Indians%20were%20brought%20home%20after%20Belgium%20was%20hit%20by%20terrorist%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20In%202016%20Operation%20Sankat%20Mochan%20was%20launched%20to%20evacuate%20Indians%20amid%20South%20Sudanese%20Civil%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20evacuation%20is%20a%20story%20of%20India's%20new%20found%20confidence%20in%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20its%20great%20strides%20and%20novel%20clarity%20of%20vision%2C%20determination%2C%20policy%20implementation%20and%20strong%20political%20will%20to%20take%20right%20calls%20in%20toughest%20of%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sanjay%20Singh%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20based%20in%20Delhi)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701351600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fuaasc8ks_uttarakhand-tunnel-collapse-reuters_625x300_29_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-tunnel-rescue-is-the-story-of-new-india-4621814%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20evacuation%20is%20a%20story%20of%20India's%20new%20found%20confidence%20in%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20its%20great%20strides%20%26amp%3B%20novel%20clarity%20of%20vision%2C%20determination%2C%20policy%20implementation%20and%20strong%20political%20will%20to%20take%20right%20calls%20in%20toughest%20of%20situations%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-tunnel-rescue-is-the-story-of-new-india-4621814%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-tunnel-rescue-is-the-story-of-new-india-4621814%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-tunnel-rescue-is-the-story-of-new-india-4621814%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Four%20migrants%20die%20after%20being%20thrown%20from%20speedboat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701351600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F768x432%2Fskynews-cadiz-spain-migrants_6377657.jpg%3F20231130143217%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffour-migrants-die-after-being-thrown-from-speedboat-off-spanish-coast-13019600%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20migrants%20have%20died%20aft