ents%2Fkissinger-in-the-middle-east%2F%5C%22%3EMiddle%20East%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.history.com%2Fnews%2Fhenry-kissinger-vietnam-war-legacy%5C%22%3ESoutheast%20Asia%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Sometimes%20the%20fallout%20%E2%80%93%20and%20it%20was%20that%20%E2%80%93%20lasted%20decades%3B%20in%20some%20places%2C%20it%20continues%20to%20be%20felt%20today.%20Nowhere%20is%20that%20more%20true%20than%20in%20Cambodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%E2%80%99m%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsearch.asu.edu%2Fprofile%2F4031078%5C%22%3Escholar%20of%20the%20political%20economy%20of%20Cambodia%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%2C%20as%20a%20child%2C%20escaped%20the%20brutal%20Khmer%20Rouge%20regime%20with%20four%20siblings%2C%20thanks%20in%20large%20part%20to%20the%20cunning%20and%20determination%20of%20my%20mother.%20In%20both%20a%20professional%20and%20personal%20sense%2C%20I%20am%20aware%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheintercept.com%2F2023%2F05%2F23%2Fhenry-kissinger-cambodia-bombing-survivors%2F%5C%22%3Enear%2050-year%20impact%3C%2Fa%3E%20Kissinger%E2%80%99s%20policies%20during%20the%20Vietnam%20War%20have%20had%20on%20the%20country%20of%20my%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20the%20murderous%20regime%20that%20forced%20my%20family%20to%20leave%20was%2C%20in%20part%2C%20encouraged%20by%20Kissinger%E2%80%99s%20policies.%20The%20cluster%20bombs%20dropped%20on%20Cambodia%20under%20Kissinger%E2%80%99s%20watch%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.the-monitor.org%2Fen-gb%2Freports%2F2023%2Fcambodia%2Fimpact.aspx%5C%22%3Econtinue%20to%20destroy%20the%20lives%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20any%20man%2C%20woman%2C%20or%20child%20who%20happens%20across%20them.%20Indeed%2C%20when%20the%20current%20U.S.%20administration%20announced%20its%20intention%20in%202023%20to%20provide%20cluster%20bombs%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20Cambodia%20was%20quick%20to%20call%20out%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fasia%2Fsoutheast-asia%2Farticle%2F3227129%2Fukraine-should-shun-us-cluster-bombs-learn-cambodias-painful-experience-pm-hun-sen%5C%22%3Elingering%20damage%20the%20munition%20causes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Island%20of%20peace%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECounterfactuals%20are%20not%20the%20best%20tool%20for%20the%20historian%3B%20no%20one%20can%20say%20how%20Cambodia%20would%20have%20developed%20were%20it%20not%20for%20the%20Vietnam%20War%20and%20US%20intervention%20in%20Southeast%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20prior%20to%20the%20US%20bombing%20of%20Cambodia%2C%20the%20country%20was%20touted%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F1997%2F09%2F01%2Fworld%2Fin-cambodia-king-sihanouk-once-more-moves-deftly-among-powers.html%5C%22%3EIsland%20of%20Peace%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20by%20then-leader%20Prince%20Norodom%20Sihanouk%2C%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Farchives%2Fla-xpm-1991-11-08-me-813-story.html%5C%22%3Edeveloping%20economy%20and%20relative%20stability%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Cambodia%20gained%20independence%20from%20its%20French%20colonial%20masters%20in%201953%2C%20Sihanouk%20presided%20over%20what%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fbooks%2Fabs%2Fviolence-and-the-civilising-process-in-cambodia%2Fgolden-years-of-sihanoukism-19551966%2F14A4A3B5B9AF2C9846BCDF518302B5D8%5C%22%3Eseen%20as%20a%20golden%20age%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Cambodia.%20Even%20Lee%20Kuan%20Yew%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20modern-day%20Singapore%2C%20visited%20Cambodia%20to%20learn%20lessons%20on%20nation-building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%E2%80%99s%20independence%20from%20France%20did%20not%20require%20any%20hard%20fight.%20Neighbouring%20Vietnam%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20gained%20independence%20only%20after%20the%20bitter%20anti-colonial%20First%20Indochina%20War%2C%20which%20concluded%20with%20a%20rout%20of%20French%20troops%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhistory.state.gov%2Fmilestones%2F1953-1960%2Fdien-bien-phu%5C%22%3Eat%20%C4%90i%E1%BB%87n%20Bi%C3%AAn%20Ph%E1%BB%A7%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%201954.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Cambodia%E2%80%99s%20location%20drew%20it%20into%20the%20subsequent%20war%20between%20the%20newly%20independent%20communist%20North%20Vietnam%20and%20the%20US-backed%20South%20Vietnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECambodia%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20officially%20a%20party%20in%20the%20Vietnam%20War%2C%20with%20Sihanouk%20declaring%20the%20country%20neutral.%20But%20Washington%20looked%20for%20ways%20to%20disrupt%20communist%20North%20Vietnamese%20operations%20along%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nga.mil%2Fdefining-moments%2FHo_Chi_Minh_Trail.html%5C%22%3EHo%20Chi%20Minh%20Trail%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20which%20cut%20across%20Cambodia%E2%80%99s%20east%2C%20with%20Sihanouk%E2%80%99s%20blessing%2C%20and%20allowed%20the%20resupply%20of%20North%20Vietnamese%20troops%20on%20Cambodian%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKissinger%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98menu%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKissinger%20was%20the%20chief%20architect%20of%20the%20plan%20to%20disrupt%20that%20supply%20line%2C%20and%20what%20he%20came%20up%20with%20was%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vietnamwar50th.com%2F1969-1971_vietnamization%2FOperation-MENU-Begins%2F%5C%22%3EOperation%20Menu%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%20The%20secret%20carpet-bombing%20campaign%20%E2%80%93%20with%20breakfast%2C%20lunch%2C%20dinner%2C%20snack%2C%20dessert%2C%20and%20supper%20representing%20different%20targets%20and%20missions%20within%20Cambodia%20%E2%80%93%20was%20confirmed%20at%20a%20meeting%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%20on%20March%2017%2C%201969.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nixonlibrary.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fvirtuallibrary%2Fdocuments%2Fhaldeman-diaries%2F37-hrhd-journal-vol01-19690317.pdf%5C%22%3Ediary%20entry%20of%20Richard%20Nixon%E2%80%99s%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20H.%20R.%20Haldeman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reads%3A%20%E2%80%9C%20%E2%80%A6%20Historic%20day.%20K%5Bissinger%5D%E2%80%98s%20%E2%80%98Operation%20Breakfast%E2%80%99%20finally%20came%20off%20at%202%3A00%20pm%20our%20time.%20K%20really%20excited%2C%20as%20is%20P%5Bresident%5D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30154233%2F52830590697_b316c750b7_o.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30154233%2F52830590697_b316c750b7_o.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30154233%2F52830590697_b316c750b7_o-300x227.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30154233%2F52830590697_b316c750b7_o-1024x774.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687106%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22907%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPresidential%20adviser%20Henry%20Kissinger%2C%20right%2C%20talks%20with%20members%20of%20the%20North%20Vietnam%20delegation%20after%20initialing%20of%20the%20Vietnam%20peace%20agreement%20was%20signed%20in%20Paris%20on%20Jan.%2024%2C%201973.%20From%20left%20are%20Nguyen%20Co%20Thach%2C%20Vice%20Minister%20for%20Foreign%20Affairs%3B%20Xuan%20Thuy%2C%20chief%20of%20the%20delegation%20to%20the%20Paris%20talks%3B%20Nguyen%20Dinh%20Phuong%2C%20interpreter%3B%20Le%20Duc%20Tho%2C%20special%20adviser%20to%20the%20delegation%20in%20Paris%3B%20and%20Kissinger.%20Photo%3A%20flickr.com%2Fmanhhai%2FCC%20BY%202.0%20DEED%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nixonlibrary.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fvirtuallibrary%2Fdocuments%2Fhaldeman-diaries%2F37-hrhd-journal-vol01-19690318.pdf%5C%22%3Efollowing%20day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Haldeman%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%9CK%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Operation%20Breakfast%E2%80%99%20a%20great%20success.%20He%20came%20beaming%20in%20with%20the%20report%2C%20very%20productive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20began%20four%20years%20of%20Kissinger%E2%80%99s%20legally%20dubious%20campaign%20in%20Cambodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20Kissinger%2C%20Cambodia%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Csideshow%2C%E2%80%9D%20to%20use%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frowman.com%2FISBN%2F9780815412243%2FSideshow-Kissinger-Nixon-and-the-Destruction-of-Cambodia-Revised-Edition%5C%22%3Etitle%20of%20William%20Shawcross%E2%80%99%20damning%20book%3C%2Fa%3E%20exposing%20the%20story%20of%20America%E2%80%99s%20secret%20war%20with%20Cambodia%20from%201969%20to%201973.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20period%2C%20the%20US%20bombing%20of%20neutral%20Cambodia%20saw%20an%20estimated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgsp.yale.edu%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fwalrus_cambodiabombing_oct06.pdf%5C%22%3E2%2C756%2C941%20tons%20of%20ordnance%20dropped%20on%20113%2C716%20targets%20in%20the%20country%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecret%20and%20illegal%20war%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKissinger%20and%20others%20in%20the%20White%20House%20tried%20to%20keep%20the%20campaign%20from%20the%20public%20for%20as%20long%20as%20they%20could%2C%20for%20good%20reason.%20It%20came%20as%20public%20opinion%20in%20the%20US%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2F2009%2F11%2F23%2Fpolling-wars-hawks-vs-doves%2F%5C%22%3Eturning%20against%20American%20involvement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20bombing%20campaign%20is%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frowman.com%2FISBN%2F9780815412243%2FSideshow-Kissinger-Nixon-and-the-Destruction-of-Cambodia-Revised-Edition%5C%22%3Econsidered%20illegal%20under%20international%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20many%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20to%20Kissinger%2C%20the%20ends%20%E2%80%93%20containing%20communism%20%E2%80%93%20seemingly%20justified%20the%20means%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20cost.%20And%20the%20cost%20to%20Cambodians%20was%20huge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20resulted%20in%20the%20direct%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgsp.yale.edu%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fwalrus_cambodiabombing_oct06.pdf%5C%22%3Edeaths%20of%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20Cambodians%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20the%20US%20government%20keeping%20the%20bombings%20secret%20at%20the%20time%2C%20comprehensive%20data%20and%20documentation%20are%20limited.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.irrawaddy.com%2Farticle.php%3Fart_id%3D2412%5C%22%3Eestimates%20on%20the%20number%20of%20deaths%3C%2Fa%3E%20range%20from%20as%20few%20as%2024%2C000%20to%20as%20many%20as%20a%20million.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pbs.org%2Ffrontlineworld%2Fstories%2Fcambodia%2Ftl02.html%5C%22%3EMost%20estimates%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.irrawaddy.com%2Farticle.php%3Fart_id%3D2412%5C%22%3Eput%20the%20death%20toll%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsites.tufts.edu%2Fatrocityendings%2F2015%2F08%2F07%2Fcambodia-u-s-bombing-civil-war-khmer-rouge%2F%5C%22%3Ein%20the%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKissinger%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20also%20destabilised%20Cambodia%2C%20leaving%20it%20vulnerable%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcla.umn.edu%2Fchgs%2Fholocaust-genocide-education%2Fresource-guides%2Fcambodia%5C%22%3Ethe%20horrors%20to%20come%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20capital%2C%20Phnom%20Penh%2C%20ballooned%20in%20population%20because%20of%20the%20displacement%20of%20more%20than%20a%20million%20rural%20citizens%20fleeing%20U.S.%20bombs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20bombing%20of%20Cambodian%20citizens%20contributed%20to%20an%20erosion%20of%20trust%20in%20Camodia%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20and%20put%20into%20question%20Sihanouk%E2%80%99s%20policy%20of%20allowing%20the%20North%20Vietnamese%20access%20through%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20east.%20On%20March%2018%2C%201970%2C%20Sihanouk%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthediplomat.com%2F2020%2F03%2Fremembering-cambodias-1970-coup%2F%5C%22%3Eousted%20in%20a%20coup%20d%E2%80%99etat%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20replaced%20by%20the%20US-friendly%20Lon%20Nol.%20Direct%20US%20involvement%20in%20the%20coup%20has%20never%20been%20proven%2C%20but%20certainly%2C%20opponents%20to%20Lon%20Nol%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fmywarwithcia00noro%5C%22%3Esaw%20the%20hand%20of%20the%20CIA%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ousted%20Sihanouk%20called%20on%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20rural%20masses%20to%20support%20his%20coalition%20government%20in%20exile%2C%20which%20included%20the%20Khmer%20Rouge.%20Until%20then%2C%20the%20Khmer%20Rouge%20had%20been%20a%20ragtag%20army%20with%20only%20revolutionary%20fantasies.%20But%20with%20Sihanouk%E2%80%99s%20backing%2C%20they%20grew.%20As%20journalist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorker.com%2Fnews%2Fnews-desk%2Fthe-fantasy-of-king-sihanouk%5C%22%3EPhilip%20Gourevitch%20noted%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CHis%20name%20became%20the%20Khmer%20Rouge%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20recruitment%20tool.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Kissinger%E2%80%99s%20bombs%20also%20served%20as%20a%20recruitment%20tool.%20The%20Khmer%20Rouge%20was%20able%20to%20capitalise%20on%20the%20anger%20and%20resentment%20of%20Cambodians%20in%20the%20areas%20being%20shelled.%20Rebel%20leaders%20portrayed%20themselves%20as%20a%20force%20to%20protect%20Cambodia%20from%20foreign%20aggression%20and%20restore%20order%20and%20justice%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20ruling%20government%E2%80%99s%20massive%20corruption%20and%20pro-American%20leanings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKissinger%E2%80%99s%20bombing%20campaign%20was%20certainly%20not%20the%20only%20reason%20for%20the%20Khmer%20Rouge%E2%80%99s%20rise%2C%20but%20it%20contributed%20to%20the%20overall%20destabilisation%20of%20Cambodia%20and%20a%20political%20vacuum%20that%20the%20Khmer%20Rouge%20was%20able%20to%20exploit%20and%20eventually%20seize%20power%20%E2%80%93%20which%20it%20did%20in%201975%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsfi.usc.edu%2Fcollections%2Fcambodian-genocide%5C%22%3Eoverthrowing%20the%20government%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20Pol%20Pot%2C%20the%20Khmer%20Rouge%20inflicted%20unimaginable%20atrocities%20upon%20the%20Cambodian%20people.%20Its%20genocidal%20campaign%20against%20political%20opponents%2C%20Cambodian%20minorities%2C%20and%20those%20deemed%20counterrevolutionaries%20saw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsfi.usc.edu%2Fcollections%2Fcambodian-genocide%5C%22%3Ebetween%201.6%20and%203%20million%20people%20killed%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20executions%2C%20forced%20labor%20and%20starvation%20%E2%80%93%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20then%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scars%20from%20that%20period%20are%20still%20felt%20in%20Cambodia%20today.%20Recent%20research%20even%20points%20to%20the%20economic%20impact%20Kissinger%E2%80%99s%20bombs%20continue%20to%20have%20on%20farmers%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Fgraphic-detail%2F2021%2F03%2F20%2Famerican-bombing-50-years-ago-still-shapes-cambodian-agriculture%5C%22%3Ewho%20avoid%20richer%2C%20darker%20soil%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20fears%20that%20it%20hides%20unexploded%20ordnance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnti-Americanism%20is%20no%20longer%20prevalent%20at%20the%20everyday%20level%20in%20Cambodia%3B%20indeed%2C%20the%20opposite%20is%20increasingly%20becoming%20true%20as%20China%E2%80%99s%20financial%20and%20political%20embrace%20becomes%20suffocating.%20However%2C%20anti-Americanism%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2Fasia_pacific%2Fthe-former-khmer-rouge-commander-who-still-leads-cambodia-is-again-stoking-anti-american-sentiment%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F679ea9c8-4cf6-11e8-b966-bfb0da2dad62_story.html%5C%22%3Efrequently%20used%20in%20rhetoric%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20leading%20politicians%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20agree%20with%20some%20other%20scholars%20that%20Kissinger%E2%80%99s%20bombing%20campaign%20can%20be%20definitively%20proven%20to%20have%20resulted%20in%20Khmer%20Rouge%20rule.%20But%20in%20my%20view%2C%20it%20no%20doubt%20contributed.%20Hun%20Sen%2C%20Cambodia%E2%80%99s%20autocratic%20leader%20who%20ruled%20for%2038%20years%20before%20passing%20the%20prime%20minister%20baton%20to%20his%20son%20in%20August%202023%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.culturalsurvival.org%2Fpublications%2Fcultural-survival-quarterly%2Ftalk-prime-minister-hun-sen%5C%22%3Ecited%20the%20US%20bombing%20of%20his%20birthplace%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20reason%20he%20joined%20the%20Khmer%20Rouge.%20Many%20others%20joined%20for%20similar%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20such%2C%20the%20devastating%20impact%20of%20Kissinger%E2%80%99s%20policies%20in%20Cambodia%20cannot%20be%20overstated%20%E2%80%93%20they%20contributed%20to%20the%20unraveling%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20social%20fabric%20and%20the%20suffering%20of%20its%20people%2C%20leaving%20behind%20a%20legacy%20of%20trauma.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F209353%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fprofiles%2Fsophal-ear-1450869%5C%22%3ESophal%20Ear%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Associate%20Professor%20in%20the%20Thunderbird%20School%20of%20Global%20Management%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Finstitutions%2Farizona-state-university-730%5C%22%3EArizona%20State%20University%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3Eunder%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fhenry-kissingers-bombing-campaign-likely-killed-hundreds-of-thousands-of-cambodians-and-set-path-for-the-ravages-of-the-khmer-rouge-209353%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701342010000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30153809%2F52259586497_c299f167c9_o.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhow-henry-kissingers-bombing-campaign-killed-thousands-destabilised-cambodia-for-long%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22To%20Kissinger%2C%20Cambodia%20was%20a%20'sideshow'%20during%20the%20Vietnam%20War%2C%20exposing%20the%20story%20of%20America's%20secret%20war%20with%20Cambodia%20from%201969%20to%201973.%20The%20US%20bombing%20of%20neutral%20Cambodia%20saw%20an%20estimated%202%2C756%2C941%20tons%E2%80%89of%20ordnance%20dropped%20on%20113%2C716%20targets%20in%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhow-henry-kissingers-bombing-campaign-killed-thousands-destabilised-cambodia-for-long%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nepal%20becomes%20first%20South%20Asian%20country%20to%20register%20same-sex%20marriage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701340680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F70x70%2Fskynews-nepal-same-sex-marriage_6377470.jpg%3F20231130114111%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fnepal-becomes-first-south-asian-country-to-register-first-same-sex-marriage-13019480%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nepal%20has%20become%20the%20first%20South%20Asian%20country%20to%20register%20a%20same-sex%20marriage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fnepal-becomes-first-south-asian-country-to-register-first-same-sex-marriage-13019480%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fnepal-becomes-first-south-asian-country-to-register-first-same-sex-marriage-13019480%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fnepal-becomes-first-south-asian-country-to-register-first-same-sex-marriage-13019480%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Raids%2C%20Seizures%2C%20Searches%3A%20How%20Central%20Agencies%20Have%20Taken%20Poll%20Position%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30145920%2FUntitled-design-13.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20run-up%20to%20the%20assembly%20polls%20saw%20yet%20another%20round%20of%20central%20investigation%20agencies%20descending%20on%20opposition%20leaders%20in%20one%20case%20or%20another.%20The%20timing%20of%20such%20raids%20were%20questioned%20by%20many%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20when%20investigation%20agencies%20are%20increasingly%20being%20seen%20as%20aiding%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20political%20interests.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20allowed%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20to%20conduct%20searches%20and%20seizures%20of%20property%20without%20a%20formal%20complaint%20in%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20cases%2C%20effectively%20presuming%20the%20accused%20person%20to%20be%20guilty.%20A%20three-judge%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20A.M.%20Khanwilkar%20broadened%20the%20investigative%20powers%20of%20the%20ED%20by%20upholding%20the%20constitutionality%20of%20several%20contentious%20sections%20of%20the%20Act.%20Since%20then%2C%20however%2C%20the%20agency%20has%20targeted%20opposition%20leaders%20particularly%20during%20election%20campaigns%2C%20raising%20grave%20doubts%20about%20its%20autonomy.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EED%E2%80%99s%20latest%20round%20of%20searches%20and%20seizures%20have%2C%20again%2C%20been%20directed%20against%20important%20opposition%20leaders%20of%20states%20which%20are%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20high-pitched%20electoral%20battles%2C%20with%20BJP%20among%20the%20principal%20players.%20Here%20are%20a%20few%20examples.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERajasthan%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%20raided%20the%20Jaipur%20and%20Sikar%20premises%20of%20Pradesh%20Congress%20President%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20Govind%20Singh%20Dotasra%2C%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20October%2C%20when%20he%20was%20busy%20campaigning.%20No%20official%20statement%20was%20issued%20by%20the%20ED%20but%20it%20came%20to%20be%20known%20that%20the%20searches%20were%20conducted%20in%20Dotasra%E2%80%99s%20houses%20in%20an%20alleged%20teachers%E2%80%99s%20entrance%20exam%20leak%20case.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlong%20with%20him%2C%20properties%20of%20another%20Congress%20MLA%20%E2%80%93%20Om%20Prakash%20Hudla%2C%20from%20the%20Mahua%20seat%20in%20Dausa%20%E2%80%93%20were%20also%20searched.%20Interestingly%2C%20paper%20leaks%20in%20service%20selection%20entrance%20examinations%20was%20one%20of%20the%20primary%20issues%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20been%20raising%20against%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot-led%20Congress%20state%20government.%20Later%20in%20November%20Dotasra%E2%80%99s%20son%20Avinash%20and%20Abhilash%20also%20received%20summons%20from%20the%20ED.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20son%20Vaibhav%20Gehlot%20also%20received%20ED%E2%80%99s%20summons%2C%20prompting%20the%20chief%20minister%20to%20compare%20the%20ED%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctiddi%20dal%E2%80%9D%20(locusts)%20obeying%20their%20masters%2C%20meaning%20the%20BJP.%20Gehlot%20said%20that%20the%20ED%20has%20been%20conducting%20raids%20against%20Congress%20leaders%20and%20workers%2C%20and%20those%20associated%20with%20the%20party%2C%20almost%20everyday%20amidst%20the%20election%20campaign.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20raids%2C%20Dotasra%20said%20that%20the%20ED%20officials%20could%20not%20find%20any%20cash%20or%20illegal%20documents%20from%20his%20premises%2C%20and%20yet%20seized%20his%20and%20his%20sons%E2%80%99%20phones%20and%20pen%20drive.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20search%20warrant%20was%20in%20the%20name%20of%20his%20son%20Avinash%2C%20who%20is%20an%20accounts%20officer.%20Reports%20indicate%20that%20the%20ED%20has%20been%20probing%20Dotasra%E2%80%99s%20links%20with%20a%20coaching%20institute%20Kalam%20academy%2C%20but%20the%20PCC%20chief%20said%20neither%20he%20nor%20his%20sons%20have%20any%20connection%20with%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20son%20was%20also%20reportedly%20called%20by%20the%20ED%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20Foreign%20Exchange%20Management%20Act%20(FEMA)%20case%20against%20a%20hospitality%20group%20called%20Triton%20Hotels%20%26amp%3B%20Resorts%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20early%20November%2C%20the%20ED%20also%20conducted%20searches%20of%2025%20premises%20in%20an%20alleged%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20scam%20being%20probed%20under%20the%20PMLA.%20The%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20is%20a%20union%20government%20scheme%20to%20provide%20potable%20water%20through%20tap%20in%20every%20household.The%20ED%20raided%20state%20minister%20Mahesh%20Joshi%E2%80%99s%20properties%20and%20the%20premises%20of%20additional%20chief%20secretary%20in%20the%20public%20health%20engineering%20department%20Subodh%20Agarwal.%20Along%20with%20him%2C%20multiple%20other%20raids%20by%20the%20ED%20happened%20in%20the%20properties%20of%20engineers%2C%20contractors%2C%20government%20officials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20scam%20was%20reported%20when%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20Anti-Corruption%20Bureau%20filed%20an%20FIR%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20BJP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Kirodi%20Lal%20Meena%20who%20alleged%20a%20Rs%2020%2C000%20crore%20scam%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20scheme.%20The%20FIR%20alleged%20that%20two%20companies%20Shree%20Shyam%20Tubewell%20Company%20and%20Shree%20Ganpati%20Tubewell%20Company%20paid%20bribes%20to%20public%20servants%20to%20cover%20up%20irregularities%20and%20inflate%20bills%20for%20the%20work%20done%20by%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20in%20July%202020%2C%20when%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20was%20facing%20revolt%20from%20his%20colleague%20Sachin%20Pilot%2C%20the%20ED%20had%20raided%20the%20premises%20associated%20with%20the%20CM%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20Agrasen%20Gehlot%2C%20and%20his%20company%20Anupam%20Krishi%20in%20a%20case%20related%20to%20alleged%20diversion%20of%20fertilisers%20during%202007-2009.%20Agrasen%20has%20been%20questioned%20by%20the%20ED%20many%20times%2C%20even%20as%20the%20case%20continues%20to%20drag%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChhattisgarh%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%E2%80%99s%20searches%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20began%20as%20early%20as%20August%2C%202023%20when%20premises%20of%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20political%20adviser%20and%20former%20journalist%20Vinod%20Verma%20and%20two%20Officers%20on%20Special%20Duty%20were%20raided%20in%20Raipur%20and%20Durg.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%2C%20following%20a%20seizure%20of%20Rs%2014.92%20crore%20in%20Raipur%20and%20Durg%2C%20the%20ED%20named%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%20its%20statement%20as%20a%20beneficiary%20of%20Rs%20508%20crore%20in%20the%20Mahadev%20betting%20app%20case%20just%20four%20days%20before%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20polls%20in%20the%20state%20on%20November%207.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20case%20itself%20was%20curious%20in%20the%20way%20it%20unfolded.%20First%2C%20the%20ED%20claimed%20that%20the%20app%E2%80%99s%20promoters%20Saurabh%20Chandrakar%20and%20Ravi%20Uppal%2C%20two%20Bhilai-based%20residents%20who%20ran%20a%20juice%20shop%2C%20ran%20a%20huge%20online%20betting%20nexus%20with%20the%20help%20of%20several%20franchises.%20The%20ED%20also%20questioned%20several%20Hindi%20film%20industry%20actors%20in%20the%20case%20that%20was%20being%20probed%20since%20July%2C%202022.%20If%20there%20was%20a%20Congress%20connection%2C%20nowhere%20did%20it%20present%20itself.%20However%2C%20just%20before%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20released%20a%20video%20clip%20in%20which%20a%20person%20named%20Shubham%20Soni%20claimed%20to%20be%20real%20owner%20of%20the%20online%20betting%20app%20and%20alleged%20that%20he%20had%20paid%20Rs%20508%20crore%20as%20bribe%20to%20Baghel%20through%20his%20media%20advisor%20and%20an%20IPS%20officer%20to%20seek%20protection%20from%20any%20punitive%20action.%20Soni%20also%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20told%20by%20Baghel%20to%20flee%20to%20Dubai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoon%20after%2C%20the%20ED%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-ed-contrasting-approach-bhupesh-baghel-devendra-tomar%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereleased%20a%20statement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20naming%20Baghel%20as%20an%20accused%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20video%20released%20by%20Soni.%20It%20also%20claimed%20that%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20name%20propped%20up%20in%20a%20statement%20made%20by%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccash%20courier%E2%80%9D%20arrested%20in%20Raipur%20with%20possession%20of%20around%20Rs%205%20crore.%20But%20the%20agency%20added%20that%20all%20these%20accusations%20%E2%80%9Care%20a%20subject%20matter%20of%20investigation%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20Congress%20slammed%20such%20accusations%20as%20serving%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20interests%20and%20tarnishing%20the%20popular%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20image%2C%20Baghel%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20never%20met%20any%20of%20the%20three%20people%20%E2%80%93%20Chandrakar%2C%20Uppal%2C%20and%20Soni%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20ED%20mentioned.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20if%20there%20was%20any%20merit%20to%20the%20accusations%2C%20the%20ED%20should%20show%20concrete%20proof.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStartlingly%2C%20days%20after%20the%20elections%20were%20over%2C%20Asim%20Das%2C%20the%20alleged%20cash%20courier%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20Raipur%20with%20around%20Rs%205%20crore%20and%20whose%20statement%20was%20the%20basis%20of%20implicating%20Baghel%20in%20the%20Mahadev%20betting%20app%20case%2C%20wrote%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-betting-app-case-courier-held-by-ed-denies-delivering-cash-to-politicians%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20letter%20to%20the%20Special%20Court%2C%20Raipur%20and%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20Director%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20saying%20that%20he%20never%20delivered%20any%20cash%20to%20politicians%20and%20that%20he%20was%20being%20framed%20in%20a%20conspiracy.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20had%20visited%20Dubai%20to%20meet%20his%20childhood%20friend%20Soni%20regarding%20investments%20in%20his%20construction%20business%20and%20indicated%20that%20the%20cash%20seized%20from%20him%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20betting%20app.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20ED%20also%20arrested%20state%20ASI%20Chandrabhushan%20Verma%2C%20businessman%20Satish%20Chandrakar%2C%20and%20alleged%20hawala%20operators%20Anil%20Dammani%20and%20Suni%20Dammani.%20The%20ED%2C%20following%20the%20raids%2C%20claimed%20that%20%E2%80%9Chigh-ranking%20officials%20connected%20with%20the%20CMO%20(Chief%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office)%20received%20kickbacks%20to%20allow%20illegal%20online%20betting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20were%20raids%20in%20other%20cases%2C%20too%2C%20by%20the%20ED.%20The%20agency%20conducted%20searches%20and%20seizures%20in%2015%20different%20places%20in%20October%20when%20it%20allied%20that%20state%20rice%20millers%20association%20in%20cahoots%20with%20officers%20of%20state%E2%80%99s%20Marketing%20Federation%20Ltd%20(MARKFED)%20illegally%20increased%20the%20price%20of%20paddy%20to%20an%20exorbitant%20Rs%20120%20per%20quintal%20after%20%E2%80%9Chigher%20powers%E2%80%9D%20were%20bribed%20with%20Rs%20175%20crore.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%20had%20made%20similar%20raids%20and%20arrested%20persons%20in%20the%20coal%20levy%20commission%20case%2C%20allegedly%20involving%20Rs%20540%20crore%20and%20illegal%20liquor%20sale%20which%20allegedly%20cost%20the%20state%20exchequer%20Rs%202160%20crore.%20In%20both%20cases%2C%20the%20ED%20claimed%20that%20the%20illegal%20money%20went%20to%20%E2%80%9Ca%20political%20party%E2%80%9D%20but%20did%20not%20elaborate%20on%20the%20accusation.%20In%20both%20cases%2C%20persons%20said%20to%20be%20close%20aides%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20Baghel%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fothers%2Fcongress-leaders-under-ed-s-scanner-in-chhattisgarh-101678190531626.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewere%20arrested%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%20made%20an%20arrest%20in%20August%20in%20an%20alleged%20Rs%20354%20crore%20bank%20fraud%20case%20involving%20many%20influential%20people%20associated%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20including%20Ratul%20Puri%2C%20the%20nephew%20of%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20Kamal%20Nath.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20had%20booked%20Ratul%20Puri%2C%20his%20father%20Deepak%20Puri%2C%20mother%20Nita%20in%20another%20case%20that%20accused%20Moser%20Baer%20India%20Ltd%2C%20a%20CD%20manufacturing%20company%20owned%20by%20Puri%2C%20and%20its%20promoters%20of%20bank%20fraud%20from%20a%20loan%20taken%20from%20the%20Central%20Bank%20of%20India.%20The%20ED%20also%20appears%20to%20be%20following%20the%20same%20case%20against%20Puri.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%20in%20August%202023%20also%20arrested%20a%20former%20relationship%20manager%20of%20the%20Bank%20of%20Singapore%20Nitin%20Bhatnagar%20in%20the%20PMLA%20case%20against%20Moser%20Baer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20leaders%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20ED%20and%20the%20income%20tax%20department%20were%20trying%20to%20indict%20multiple%20Congress%20workers%20and%20associates%20under%20the%20scanner%20to%20help%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20elections..%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20are%20getting%20information%20through%20newspapers%20that%20the%20offices%20of%20Income%20Tax%20and%20ED%20are%20being%20opened%20at%20different%20places%E2%80%A6Officials%20are%20being%20posted%E2%80%A6They%20are%20raiding%20the%20ruling%20(Congress)%20regime%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20told%20reporters%20in%20Bhopal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20ED%2C%20IT%20offices%20are%20being%20opened%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20they%20should%20raid%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20ministers%20and%20their%20favourite%20officers%2C%20but%20as%20per%20the%20news%20being%20received%2C%20they%20are%20planning%20to%20target%20the%20Congress%20and%20opposition%20leaders%20in%20MP%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETelangana%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20southern%20state%20of%20Telangana%2C%20the%20ED%20sent%20fresh%20summons%20to%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20MLC%20K.%20Kavitha%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20daughter%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20K.Chandrasekhar%20Rao%2C%20in%20the%20Delhi%20excise%20policy%20case%2C%20weeks%20before%20the%20assembly%20polls.%20She%20has%20received%20ED%E2%80%99s%20summons%20in%20the%20case%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0The%20new%20excise%20policy%20introduced%20by%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20government%20in%20which%20849%20liquor%20shops%20were%20allocated%20to%20private%20firms%20was%20scrapped%20by%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20government%20after%20Delhi%20L-G%20Vinay%20Kumar%20Saxena%20recommended%20a%20CBI%20inquiry%2C%20citing%20irregularities%20in%20the%20policy%E2%80%99s%20implementation.%20AAP%20leaders%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%20have%20already%20been%20arrested%20in%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%20alleged%20that%20Kavitha%2C%20too%2C%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CSouth%20Group%E2%80%9D%20that%20paid%20at%20least%20Rs%20100%20crore%20in%20bribes%20to%20AAP%20through%20AAP%20worker%20and%20businessman%20Vijay%20Nair%20who%20has%20already%20been%20arrested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlong%20with%20Kavitha%2C%20various%20other%20BRS%20functionaries%20also%20faced%20ED%E2%80%99s%20raids.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20week%20before%20polling%2C%20the%20ED%20also%20swooped%20down%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2Ftelangana-polls-ed-raids-properties-of-congress-candidate-g-vivek%2Farticleshow%2F105373501.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20MLA%20candidate%20G.Vivek%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20Rs%208%20crore%20transaction%20between%20his%20company%20and%20one%20Vigilance%20Security%20Services%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%20The%20ED%20claimed%20that%20the%20transferred%20amount%20originated%20from%20an%20unidentified%20bank%20account.%20Searches%20were%20conducted%20on%20November%2020%20at%20various%20locations%20owned%20by%20Vivek%2C%20Congress%20MLA%20candidate%20from%20Chennu%20seat.%20Incidentally%2C%20Vivek%20had%20recently%20quit%20the%20BJP%20to%20join%20the%20Congress%20and%20is%20the%20richest%20candidate%20in%20the%20fray.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20I-T%20department%20also%20conducted%20searches%20at%20Vivek%E2%80%99s%20premises.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20I-T%20department%20and%20the%20ED%20had%20raided%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Fnation%2Fpolitics%2F021123%2Fincome-tax-raids-on-congress-and-brs-leaders-in-hyderabad.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20premises%20of%20Congress%20candidates%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Kichannagari%20Lakshma%20Reddy%20of%20Maheswaram%20and%20Ponguleti%20Srinivasa%20Reddy%20of%20Palair%20in%20different%20cases%20of%20financial%20fraud.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECuriously%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20used%20most%20of%20these%20raids%20as%20vehicles%20to%20advance%20its%20anti-corruption%20political%20rhetoric%20and%20have%20attacked%20the%20opposition%20parties%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20polls.%20In%20many%20of%20these%20cases%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20more%20than%20the%20ED%2C%20has%20revealed%20the%20charges%20against%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20in%20its%20press%20briefings.%20How%20the%20BJP%20managed%20to%20get%20the%20details%20even%20before%20the%20ED%20revealed%20them%20was%20debated%20in%20political%20circles%20quite%20vigorously.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20didn%E2%80%99t%20conduct%20any%20raids%20in%20Mizoram.%20The%20election%20in%20the%20state%20is%20between%20the%20incumbent%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20or%20MNF%20and%20the%20other%20seven-party%20regional%20alliance%2C%20the%20Zoram%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movement.%20The%20BJP%20has%20one%20MLA%20in%20the%20state%20at%20present%20and%20analysts%20say%20it%20does%20not%20have%20any%20major%20electoral%20stakes%20here%2C%20as%20it%20depends%20more%20or%20less%20on%20its%20regional%20allies.%20Narendra%20Modi%20cancelled%20his%20election%20rally%20here.%20The%20Congress%20used%20to%20be%20an%20important%20player%20but%20has%20now%20shrunk%2C%20with%20just%205%20MLAs%20in%20the%20outgoing%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehad%20earlier%20reported%20that%20almost%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2F95-of-political-leaders-investigated-by-cbi-ed-are-opposition-leaders-non-bjp-parties-tell-supreme-court-224653%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E95%25%20of%20the%20cases%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20probed%20by%20the%20ED%20and%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20against%20political%20leaders%20are%20from%20the%20opposition.%20Although%20the%20ED%20claims%20that%20it%20has%20a%20high%20conviction%20rate%20of%2096%25%2C%20the%20figures%20appear%20to%20be%20misplaced%20if%20one%20factors%20in%20the%20number%20of%20cases%20it%20has%20closed%20since%202005.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%20registered%205%2C906%20cases%20until%20March%202023%20but%20completed%20the%20probe%20and%20filed%20a%20chargesheet%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fed-is-claiming-it-has-a-high-conviction-rate-but-its-closed-only-25-cases-since-2005%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eonly%201%2C142%20cases%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20out%20of%20which%20it%20has%20disposed%20of%20only%2025%20cases%2C%20a%20mere%200.42%20of%20the%20total%20number%20of%20cases.%20Of%20those%2025%20cases%2C%20the%20ED%20has%20managed%20convictions%20in%2024%20cases%2C%20which%20is%20around%2096%25%20conviction%20rate%20as%20claimed%20by%20the%20agency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20response%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20ED%20had%20earlier%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-the-enforcement-directorate-has-become-an-excessive-directorate%5C%22%3Edenied%20all%20allegations%20of%20bias%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexpress-exclusive%2Fsince-2014-4-fold-jump-in-ed-cases-against-politicians-95-per-cent-are-from-opposition-8163060%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20four-fold%20jump%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20ED%20cases%20since%202014%3B%2095%25%20of%20those%20cases%20are%20against%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fed-scanner-aap-bjp-satyendar-jain-sanjay-raut-chidambaram-1956298-2022-05-31%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eopposition%20leaders%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701340232000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30145920%2FUntitled-design-13.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felection-opposition-leaders-raids-ed-cbi-income-tax%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22ED%E2%80%99s%20latest%20round%20of%20searches%20and%20seizures%20have%2C%20again%2C%20been%20directed%20against%20important%20opposition%20leaders%20of%20states%20which%20are%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20high-pitched%20electoral%20battles%2C%20with%20BJP%20among%20the%20principal%20players.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felection-opposition-leaders-raids-ed-cbi-income-tax%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Narrow%20Nationalism%20Has%20Won%20Over%20Cosmopolitanism%20Again%2C%20This%20Time%20in%20the%20Netherlands%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30133927%2FGeert-Wilders.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20the%201990s%2C%20Western%20political%20theorists%20began%20to%20build%20on%20the%20foundations%20of%20trade%20and%20financial%20liberalisation%20and%20globalisation%2C%20a%20structure%20of%20global%20political%20theory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20long%2C%20political%20theory%20and%20international%20relations%20had%20little%20to%20do%20with%20each%20other.%20Political%20theorists%20tended%20to%20analyse%20and%20prescribe%20for%20nationally-bounded%20sovereign%20states.%20International%20relations%20theory%20was%20preoccupied%20with%20sovereign%20nation-states%20as%20the%20primary%20units%20of%20the%20international%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20globalisation%2C%20Western%20political%20theorists%20went%20global.%20They%20realised%20that%20in%20an%20interconnected%20globalised%20world%2C%20both%20problems%20and%20the%20solutions%20to%20these%20problems%20have%20to%20be%20global.%20They%20also%20showed%20immense%20concern%20for%20poverty%20in%20countries%20of%20the%20global%20south%2C%20and%20inequalities%20between%20the%20global%20north%20and%20the%20global%20south.%20The%20influential%20theory%20that%20emerged%20from%20Western%20academia%20was%20that%20of%20global%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ground%20for%20the%20global%20justice%20debate%20was%20inspired%20by%20a%201972%20paper%20by%20the%20utilitarian%20philosopher%20Peter%20Singer%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpersonal.lse.ac.uk%2Frobert49%2Fteaching%2Fmm%2Farticles%2FSinger_1972Famine.pdf%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Famine%2C%20Affluence%20and%20Morality%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20reputed%20journal%20%3Cem%3EPhilosophy%20and%20Public%20Affairs%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30125539%2FPeter-Singer-300x248.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30125539%2FPeter-Singer-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30125539%2FPeter-Singer-1024x846.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30125539%2FPeter-Singer.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687067%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22248%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Mal%20Vickers%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY%20SA%204.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20argued%20that%20suffering%20and%20death%20from%20a%20lack%20of%20food%2C%20shelter%20and%20medical%20care%20are%20simply%20bad.%20If%20it%20is%20within%20the%20power%20of%20the%20citizens%20of%20the%20affluent%20West%20to%20prevent%20something%20bad%20from%20happening%2C%20without%20sacrificing%20anything%20of%20comparable%20moral%20importance%2C%20they%20are%20morally%20obliged%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20does%20not%20matter%20that%20people%20who%20suffer%20for%20avoidable%20reasons%20are%20distant%20or%20proximate%2C%20or%20whether%20they%20are%20fellow%20nationals%20or%20needy%20foreigners.%20The%20need%20of%20strangers%20is%20as%20morally%20compelling%20as%20the%20need%20of%20neighbours%20or%20fellow%20citizens.%C2%A0%20It%20also%20does%20not%20matter%20that%20other%20people%20do%20or%20do%20not%20contribute%20their%20mite%20to%20the%20alleviation%20of%20poverty%20and%20misery%3B%20individuals%20should%20take%20on%20this%20moral%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20finally%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20donating%20to%20famine%20relief%20is%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20charity%20but%20that%20of%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20later%20work%20titled%20%3Cem%3EOne%20World%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Singer%20argued%20that%20since%20the%20world%20is%20interlinked%2C%20we%20need%20a%20transborder%20global%20ethics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImagine%2C%20he%20suggested%2C%20that%20you%20walk%20along%20a%20pond%20and%20see%20a%20small%20child%20in%20danger%20of%20drowning.%20It%20would%20be%20morally%20wrong%20not%20to%20try%20to%20save%20the%20child%20even%20if%20the%20suit%20we%20wear%20gets%20wet%20and%20is%20ruined.%20The%20cost%20is%20small%20compared%20to%20the%20good%20of%20saving%20the%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20can%20have%20special%20feelings%20for%20those%20we%20love%20or%20those%20who%20are%20close%20to%20us%2C%20but%20this%20need%20not%20prevent%20us%20from%20helping%20others.%20There%20is%20no%20great%20difference%20between%20compatriots%20and%20the%20distant%20needy.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20middle-class%20American%20should%20give%20to%20the%20global%20poor%20something%20like%20one%20percent%20of%20his%20or%20her%20annual%20income.%20Basically%2C%20Singer%20focused%20on%20moral%20choices%20between%20spending%20on%20personal%20desires%20and%20helping%20the%20needy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20number%20of%20political%20theorists%20living%20and%20working%20in%20what%20was%20once%20called%20the%20third%20world%2C%20were%20considerably%20sceptical%2C%20even%20outraged%20at%20this%20newest%20version%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98white%20man%E2%80%99s%E2%80%99%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECould%20we%20in%20the%20global%20south%20afford%20to%20wait%20for%20citizens%20of%20the%20West%20to%20recognise%20their%20obligations%20to%20the%20distant%20needy%3F%20Should%20we%20be%20doing%20so%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fpalestine-palestinians-and-the-western-liberals-burden%5C%22%3EPalestine%2C%20Palestinians%20and%20the%20Western%20Liberal%E2%80%99s%20Burden%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20it%20not%20dependent%20on%20charity.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20wrenched%20from%20the%20recalcitrant%20fists%20of%20elites%20through%20mass%20struggles%20and%20agitation.%20Despite%20some%20acrimonious%20challenges%20to%20the%20universality%20of%20global%20justice%20(for%20we%20who%20inhabit%20the%20world%20of%20the%20distant%20needy%20had%20no%20role%20to%20play%20in%20these%20theories%20except%20as%20a%20recipient)%20the%20debate%20taught%20us%20a%20valuable%20lesson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20need%20to%20expand%20the%20notion%20of%20duties%20and%20concern%20to%20people%20who%20live%20outside%20our%20borders.%20We%20should%20adopt%20a%20cosmopolitan%20approach%20towards%20human%20well-being.%20Cosmopolitanism%20moderates%20nationalist%20ambitions%20and%20opens%20many%20doors%20to%20solidarity%20across%20national%20borders.%20This%20is%20its%20virtue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20second%20decade%20of%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20the%20context%20of%20political%20theory%20had%20dramatically%20changed.%20Across%20the%20world%2C%20the%20extreme%20right-wing%20came%20to%20command%20power.%20Under%20the%20impact%20of%20right-wing%20extremism%2C%20cosmopolitanism%20was%20thrown%20out%20of%20the%20window%2C%20and%20societies%20closed%20their%20doors%20and%20windows.%20They%20were%20now%20preoccupied%20with%20hostility%20against%20minorities%2C%20immigrants%2C%20%E2%80%98outsiders%E2%80%99%20and%20neighbouring%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20imaginary%20enemy%2C%20right-wing%20populists%20told%20us%2C%20does%20not%20lurk%20on%20our%20border%20alone%2C%20it%20is%20within%20our%20own%20borders.%20Our%20fellow-citizens%20and%20those%20who%20sought%20citizenship%20became%20our%20enemies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENever%20has%20the%20shift%20from%20cosmopolitanism%20to%20a%20narrow%20and%20ugly%20nationalism%20taken%20place%20so%20rapidly%2C%20except%20in%20the%20period%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20consolidation%20of%20German%20Nazism%2C%20which%20was%20openly%20hostile%20to%20the%20internationalism%20of%20the%20Left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notion%20of%20obligation%20towards%20the%20%E2%80%98distant%20needy%E2%80%99%20or%20even%20the%20%E2%80%98proximate%20needy%E2%80%99%20who%20did%20not%20belong%20to%20our%20religious%20community%2C%20were%20replaced%20by%20duty%20towards%20our%20own%20people%20with%20whom%20we%20were%20bound%20by%20ties%20of%20religion%20or%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20distinction%20between%20cosmopolitanism%20and%20a%20nationalism%20that%20urges%20us%20to%20confine%20our%20loyalties%20to%20our%20own%2C%20came%20to%20mind%20as%20we%20read%20of%20another%20victory%20of%20the%20extreme%20right%20in%20Europe%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhow-geert-wilders-poll-victory-in-the-netherlands-reflects-european-radical-right-populism%5C%22%3Ethe%20success%20of%20Geert%20Wilder%E2%80%99s%20Party%20for%20Freedom%20(PVV)%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Netherlands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160248%2FWilders-bezoekt-Rotterdam-DSC_0218_cropped-300x187.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160248%2FWilders-bezoekt-Rotterdam-DSC_0218_cropped-300x187.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160248%2FWilders-bezoekt-Rotterdam-DSC_0218_cropped.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686091%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22187%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGeert%20Wilders.%20Photo%3A%20Wouter%20Engler%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PVV%2C%20winning%2037%20of%20the%2050%20seats%20in%20parliament%2C%20is%20now%20a%20majority%20party.%20The%20Netherlands%2C%20for%20long%20identified%20with%20centrist%20politics%2C%20has%20now%20turned%20to%20the%20right.%20The%20implications%20are%20grim%20because%20Wilder%20is%20a%20polarising%20figure.%20He%20is%20against%20immigration%2C%20Islam%20and%20the%20European%20Union.%20He%20has%20opposed%20the%20construction%20of%20mosques%2C%20advocates%20strict%20control%20on%20drugs%20and%20urges%20a%20reduction%20in%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20decades%2C%20most%20of%20Europe%20has%20been%20taken%20over%20by%20right-wing%20populists.%20Viktor%20Orban%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Hungary%2C%20has%20directed%20the%20erection%20of%20fences%20to%20keep%20out%20refugees%20from%20war-torn%20Syria%2C%20captured%20the%20judiciary%20and%20other%20institutions%2C%20has%20openly%20encouraged%20crony%20capitalism%2C%20incorporated%20Christian%20values%20into%20the%20Constitution%20and%20is%20reportedly%20against%20gender%20studies%20in%20university%20curricula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20written%20the%20standard%20text%20of%20right-wing%20authoritarianism%2Fpopulism%3A%20institutional%20capture%20and%20democratic%20backsliding.%20Right-wing%20authoritarianism%20has%20transformed%20former%20liberal%20democracies%20into%20illiberal%20electoral%20democracies.%20All%20that%20remains%20on%20the%20political%20landscape%20is%20elections.%20The%20script%20is%20surely%20familiar%20to%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20examples%20that%20come%20to%20us%20from%20Europe.%20One%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwhat-will-its-first-far-right-leader-since-wwii-mean-for-italy%5C%22%3Erise%20of%20Georgia%20Meloni%E2%80%99s%20Brothers%20of%20Italy%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Italy%3A%20nationalistic%20to%20the%20core%2C%20anti-immigrant%20and%20obsessed%20with%20state%20sovereignty.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Ffrance-far-right-marine-le-pen-2022-election%5C%22%3EThe%20increasing%20prominence%20of%20Marine%20Le%20Penn%E2%80%99s%20National%20Rally%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20France%20promises%20that%20another%20right-wing%20populist%20will%20come%20to%20power%20at%20some%20point%20in%20a%20country%20that%20expanded%20and%20popularised%20democracy%20first%20conceived%20of%20and%20implemented%20in%20Greece.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20countless%20other%20examples%20of%20right-wing%20populists%3A%20Netanyahu%20in%20Israel%20and%20Putin%20in%20Russia%2C%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20the%20former%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20of%20course%2C%20the%20current%20leaders%20of%20India.%20They%20insistently%20subvert%20democracy%2C%20erode%20liberal%20ideas%20of%20obligation%20to%20others%20simply%20because%20they%20are%20human%20beings%2C%20dismiss%20inclusiveness%20and%20pluralism%2C%20mock%20equality%20and%20dignity%2C%20tolerance%20and%20secularism%2C%20corrode%20institutions%2C%20curtail%20civil%20liberties%20and%20openly%20head-hunt%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Europe%20and%20the%20US%2C%20the%20right%20head-hunts%20refugees%20who%20have%20been%20driven%20from%20their%20homes%20by%20wars%20not%20of%20their%20own%20making.%20Europe%2C%20once%20the%20site%20of%20the%20Renaissance%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20humanism%20and%20modern%20political%20values%20such%20as%20liberty%2C%20equality%20and%20fraternity%2C%20has%20become%20a%20graveyard%20of%20all%20these%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthe-right-wing-is-on-the-rise-globally%5C%22%3EThe%20Right%20Wing%20Is%20on%20the%20Rise%20Globally%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20to%20misrecognise%20the%20fact%20that%20European%20countries%20violated%20their%20own%20values%20while%20colonising%20our%20world.%20But%20this%20is%20not%20the%20issue%20at%20hand%2C%20it%20requires%20a%20different%20story.%20The%20issue%20is%20as%20follows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Why%20does%20Globalisation%20Fuel%20Populism%3F%E2%80%99%20This%20is%20the%20title%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.annualreviews.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1146%2Fannurev-economics-070220-032416%5C%22%3Ewell-known%20essay%3C%2Fa%3E%20authored%20by%20the%20economist%20Dani%20Rodrik%20of%20Harvard%20University%20in%20the%202021%20%3Cem%3EAnnual%20Review%20of%20Economics%3C%2Fem%3E.%20There%20is%2C%20he%20suggests%2C%20compelling%20evidence%20that%20globalisation%20shocks%2C%20often%20working%20through%20culture%20and%20identity%2C%20have%20played%20an%20important%20role%20in%20driving%20up%20support%20for%20populist%20movements%20of%20the%20right-wing%20kind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20integration%20has%20produced%20domestic%20disintegration%20in%20many%20countries.%20The%20populist%20response%20seems%20to%20have%20taken%20a%20mostly%20right-wing%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20factors%20that%20intensify%20uncertainty%20amidst%20globalisation.%20Across%20the%20globe%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20consequences%20of%20globalisation%20is%20the%20dismantling%20of%20the%20welfare%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20whatever%20social%20legislation%20was%20passed%20in%20the%202004-2014%20period%20of%20UPA%20rule%20has%20been%20pulled%20to%20pieces%20by%20the%20NDA%20regime.%20The%20religious%20right-wing%20in%20the%20country%20has%20put%20into%20place%20a%20highly%20personalised%20system%20of%20the%20grant%20of%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20welfare%20is%20no%20longer%20an%20aspect%20of%20an%20appropriative%20state%3B%20it%20amounts%20to%20little%20more%20than%20the%20gift%20giving%20of%20a%20handful%20of%20grain%20and%20a%20little%20money.%20The%20grateful%20consumer%20is%20expected%20to%20show%20her%2C%20well%20gratitude%2C%20by%20casting%20a%20vote%20for%20the%20gift-giver.%20The%20citizen%2C%20as%20Yamini%20Aiyar%20puts%20it%2C%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3Elabharthi%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dismantling%20of%20the%20welfare%20state%20that%20had%20been%20built%20brick-by-brick%20by%20social%20struggles%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%20a%20sympathetic%20judiciary%2C%20has%20led%20to%20tremendous%20insecurity.%20Privatisation%20of%20assets%20to%20industrial%20houses%20openly%20aligned%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%20has%20gravely%20reduced%20government%20jobs.%20Whatever%20jobs%20are%20left%20in%20the%20government%20sector%20have%20become%20the%20object%20of%20fervent%20desire%2C%20simply%20because%20they%20promise%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20above%20all%2C%20globalisation%20brings%20a%20sense%20of%20homelessness%20because%20we%20no%20longer%20have%20a%20definite%20identity%20in%20an%20interconnected%20world.%20This%20was%20an%20identity%20that%20was%20carefully%20fashioned%20by%20the%20leaders%20of%20our%20freedom%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInto%20this%20vacuum%20stepped%20in%20the%20religious%20right%2C%20flourishing%20the%20pennant%20of%20%E2%80%98we%20versus%20them%E2%80%99%2C%20advocating%20a%20strong%20state%20and%20an%20even%20stronger%20leader%2C%20and%20urging%20us%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20main%20issue%20is%20cultural%20homogeneity%20and%20the%20marginalisation%20of%20people%20who%20do%20not%20fit%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight-wing%20populists%20are%20dangerous%20because%20their%20politics%20is%20extremist%2C%20their%20ideology%20exclusionary%2C%20their%20enmity%20to%20those%20who%20do%20not%20belong%20palpable%2C%20their%20religious%20rhetoric%20cynical%20and%20opportunistic%2C%20and%20their%20chief%20desire%20to%20divide%20people%20so%20that%20they%20can%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20only%20a%20little%20over%20three%20decades%20that%20political%20theorists%20were%20speaking%20of%20a%20cosmopolitanism%2C%20a%20concept%20that%20Indians%20were%20already%20familiar%20with%20through%20the%20creative%20writings%20of%20Rabindranath%20Tagore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20we%20speak%20the%20language%20of%20provocation%2C%20taboos%2C%20censorship%2C%20coercion%20and%20bullying.%20Globalisation%20has%20battered%20the%20notion%20of%20obligation%20to%20each%20other%20simply%20because%20as%20human%20beings%20we%20owe%20each%20other.%20We%20now%20live%20in%20a%20Hobbesian%20state%20of%20nature%2C%20which%20is%20a%20state%20of%20war%20of%20all%20against%20all.%20We%20wait%20for%20a%20Leviathan%20to%20restore%20and%20reinforce%20our%20social%20contract%20%E2%80%93%20our%20Constitution%20that%20promises%20fraternity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fneera-chandhoke%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ENeera%20Chandhoke%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0was%20a%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20at%20Delhi%20University.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701338451000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30133927%2FGeert-Wilders.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnarrow-nationalism-has-won-over-cosmopolitanism-again-this-time-in-the-netherlands%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22International%20integration%20has%20produced%20domestic%20disintegration%20in%20many%20countries.%20The%20populist%20response%2C%20including%20in%20India%2C%20seems%20to%20have%20taken%20a%20mostly%20right-wing%20form.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnarrow-nationalism-has-won-over-cosmopolitanism-again-this-time-in-the-netherlands%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Court%20Filing%20That%20Links%20Assassination%20Attempt%20to%20Indian%20Official%20'Matter%20of%20Concern'%3A%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22182025%2Fdownload-11.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India%20on%20Thursday%20said%20that%20the%20linking%20of%20an%20Indian%20official%20in%20a%20case%20filed%20by%20US%20prosecutors%20against%20an%20Indian%20citizen%20for%20directing%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20assassinate%20a%20US%20citizen%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmatter%20of%20concern%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2FOn%2520the%2520evening%2520of%2520June%252018%2520after%2520Hardeep%2520Singh%2520Nijjar%2520was%2520gunned%2520down%2520outside%2520a%2520Sikh%2520temple%2520in%2520Canada%2C%2520%5C%22%3EA%20day%20earlier%2C%20US%20prosecutors%20filed%20a%2015-page%20detailed%20indictment%3C%2Fa%3E%20alleging%20that%20an%20%E2%80%9Cidentified%20Indian%20government%20employee%E2%80%9D%20was%20behind%20a%20plot%20of%20assassinate%20a%20US%20citizen%20who%20runs%20a%20pro-Khalistan%20group%20that%20is%20banned%20by%20India.%20While%20the%20indictment%20does%20not%20name%20the%20target%2C%20it%20is%20understood%20that%20the%20attempt%20was%20made%20on%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20head%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Sikhs%20for%20Justice%E2%80%99%20NGO%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20filings%20charged%20Indian%20resident%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20who%20had%20allegedly%20been%20the%20go-between%20between%20the%20Indian%20government%20official%20(%E2%80%98CC-1%E2%80%99)%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98criminal%20associate%E2%80%99%20and%20a%20%E2%80%98hitman%E2%80%99%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20were%20actually%20working%20for%20US%20law%20enforcement%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20post-indictment%20reaction%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20regards%20the%20case%20against%20an%20individual%20that%20has%20been%20filed%20in%20a%20US%20court%2C%20allegedly%20linking%20him%20to%20an%20Indian%20official%2C%20this%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern.%20We%20have%20said%2C%20let%20me%20reiterate%2C%20that%20this%20is%20also%20contrary%20to%20government%20policy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20reiterated%20India%E2%80%99s%20characterisation%20of%20the%20US%20concerns%20as%20being%20related%20to%20criminal%20activity.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20nexus%20between%20organised%20crime%2C%20trafficking%2C%20gunrunning%20and%20extremists%20at%20an%20international%20level%20is%20a%20serious%20issue%20for%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20and%20organisations%20to%20consider%20and%20it%20is%20for%20that%20reason%20that%20a%20high-level%20inquiry%20committee%20has%20been%20constituted%20and%20we%20will%20be%20guided%20by%20its%20results%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bagchi%20said%20at%20a%20media%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MEA%20had%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20just%20ahead%20of%20release%20of%20the%20fresh%20indictment%2C%20that%20India%20had%20set%20up%20an%20inquiry%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20US%20%E2%80%98plot%E2%80%99%20on%20November%2018.%20The%20government%20had%20not%20spoken%20of%20the%20committee%20when%20the%20US%20%E2%80%98concerns%E2%80%99%20were%20first%20reported%20by%20the%20media%20%E2%80%93%20and%20then%20confirmed%20by%20the%20White%20House%20%E2%80%93%20on%20November%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20we%20have%20informed%20earlier%2C%20during%20the%20course%20of%20discussions%20with%20the%20US%20on%20bilateral%20security%20cooperation%2C%20the%20US%20side%20shared%20some%20inputs%20pertaining%20to%20nexus%20between%20organised%20criminals%2C%20gun%20runners%2C%20terrorists%20and%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20stating%20that%20%E2%80%9Cnecessary%20follow-up%20action%E2%80%9D%20will%20be%20taken%20based%20on%20the%20Enquiry%20Committee%E2%80%99s%20follow-up%2C%20Bagchi%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20cannot%20share%20any%20further%20information%20on%20such%20security%20matters.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContrasting%20India%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20concerns%20raised%20by%20US%20and%20Canada%20about%20targeting%20of%20their%20citizens%2C%20Bagchi%20continued%20with%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20tough%20stance%20against%20Ottawa.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20so%20far%20as%20Canada%20is%20concerned%2C%20we%20have%20said%20that%20they%20have%20consistently%20given%20space%20to%20anti-India%20extremists%20and%20that%20is%20actually%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20issue.%20Our%20diplomatic%20representatives%20in%20Canada%20have%20borne%20the%20brunt%20of%20this.%20So%2C%20we%20expect%20the%20Government%20of%20Canada%20to%20live%20up%20to%20its%20obligations%20under%20the%20Vienna%20Convention%20on%20Diplomatic%20Relations.%20We%20have%20also%20seen%20interference%20by%20Canadian%20diplomats%20in%20our%20internal%20affairs%20and%20that%20is%20unacceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20indictment%20filed%20by%20US%20federal%20prosecutor%20clearly%20indicated%20that%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20had%20been%20aware%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98big%20target%E2%80%99%20in%20Canada%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20night%20of%20June%2018%2C%20following%20the%20shooting%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20outside%20a%20Sikh%20temple%20in%20Canada%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-sdny%2Fpr%2Fus-attorney-announces-charges-connection-foiled-plot-assassinate-us-citizen-new-york%5C%22%3Ethe%20indictment%20stated%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CCC-1%20sent%20GUPTA%20a%20video%20clip%20showing%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20bloody%20body%20slumped%20in%20his%20vehicle%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20significant%20point%20in%20the%20court%20filing%20as%20it%20indicated%20that%20US%20authorities%20had%20obtained%20electronic%20communications%20that%20linked%20the%20Indian%20government%20official%20directly%20to%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing.%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20had%20made%20this%20claim%20of%20alleged%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20government%20agents%20in%20September%20this%20year%2C%20which%20New%20Delhi%20had%20instantly%20dismissed.%20The%20Union%20government%20took%20subsequent%20steps%20that%20led%20to%2041%20Canadian%20diplomats%20leaving%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701337983000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22182025%2Fdownload-11.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fus-court-filing-that-links-assassination-attempt-to-indian-official-matter-of-concern-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20regards%20the%20case%20against%20an%20individual%20that%20has%20been%20filed%20in%20a%20US%20court%2C%20allegedly%20linking%20him%20to%20an%20Indian%20official%2C%20this%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern.%20We%20have%20said%2C%20let%20me%20reiterate%2C%20that%20this%20is%20also%20contrary%20to%20government%20policy.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fus-court-filing-that-links-assassination-attempt-to-indian-official-matter-of-concern-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rural%20Consumption%20Sees%20Slowest%20Growth%20in%20Eight%20Quarters%20During%20July-September%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F13125046%2Fagriculture-copy.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Rural%20consumption%20experienced%20a%20mere%200.5%25%20year-on-year%20growth%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20fiscal%20year%202024%2C%20marking%20the%20slowest%20pace%20in%20eight%20quarters%2C%20a%20new%20report%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20contrasts%20with%20urban%20consumption%2C%20which%20grew%207.4%25%20in%20July-September%202023%2C%20the%20highest%20rate%20in%20four%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20analysis%20by%20Motilal%20Oswal%20Financial%20Services%20(MOFSL)%2C%20the%20tepid%20consumption%20scenario%20in%20rural%20areas%20was%20mainly%20led%20by%20sharply%20deteriorating%20reservoir%20level%2C%20the%20first%20fall%20in%20two-wheeler%20sales%20in%20six%20quarters%2C%20and%20first%20contraction%20in%20fertilizer%20sales%20in%20seven%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETractor%20sales%20also%20decreased%20for%20the%20second%20consecutive%20quarter%2C%20coupled%20with%20a%20decline%20in%20real%20farm%20exports%20for%20the%20fourth%20straight%20quarter%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fpolicy%2Feconomy-rural-consumption-tepid-q2-growth-slowest-in-8-quarters-3321097%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%2C%20citing%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20analysis%20is%20also%20supported%20by%20the%20MGNREGA%20(Mahatma%20Gandhi%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act)%20data.%20Employment%20demand%20by%20households%20under%20MGNREGA%20was%20much%20higher%20in%20the%20first%20seven%20months%20of%20FY24%20compared%20with%20FY23%20and%20FY18-20%20average%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20agency%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2022%20million%20people%20demanded%20employment%20under%20MGNREGA%20each%20in%20September%20and%20October%2C%2010-18%25%20higher%20than%20in%20the%20corresponding%20months%20of%20FY23%2C%20and%2026-31%25%20higher%20than%20the%20pre-COVID%20period%2C%20said%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHDFC%20Bank%E2%80%99s%20economist%20Swati%20Arora%20told%20the%20business%20daily%20that%20uneven%20monsoon%20led%20to%20crop%20damage%2C%20which%20weighed%20on%20rural%20consumption.%20She%20added%20that%20higher%20inflation%20added%20to%20the%20woes%20and%20also%20weighed%20on%20discretionary%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20the%20gap%20between%20rural%20and%20urban%20demand%20is%20likely%20to%20reduce%20in%20Q3%20FY24.%20She%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20pre-election%20revenue%20spending%20(such%20as%20LPG%20Price%20cut%2C%20fertiliser%20and%20LPG%20subsidy%2C%20and%20extension%20of%20free%20food%20grain%20programme)%20bodes%20well%20for%20rural%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMOFSL%E2%80%99s%20chief%20economist%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20told%20%3Cem%3EFE%20t%3C%2Fem%3Ehat%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20five%20state%20assemblies%20going%20into%20elections%20over%20the%20next%20month%20and%20general%20elections%20scheduled%20in%20May%202024%2C%20the%20hope%20of%20a%20revival%20in%20the%20rural%20sector%20is%20alive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701336616000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F13125046%2Fagriculture-copy.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Frural-consumption-sees-slowest-growth-in-eight-quarters-during-july-september-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20contrasts%20with%20urban%20consumption%2C%20which%20grew%207.4%25%20in%20July-September%202023%2C%20the%20highest%20rate%20in%20four%20quarters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire