ster%20Justin%20Trudeau%20as%20having%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20news%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20United%20States%20further%20underscores%20what%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20talking%20about%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20which%20is%20that%20India%20needs%20to%20take%20this%20seriously.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Indian%20government%20needs%20to%20work%20with%20us%20to%20ensure%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20getting%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701326809000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30121410%2FUntitled-design-12-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Findia-us-pannun-nijjar-foreign-media%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'In%20most%20cases%2C%20if%20Washington%20accuses%20a%20foreign%20government%20of%20staging%20an%20assassination%20on%20its%20soil%2C%20U.S.%20relations%20with%20that%20government%20would%20plunge%20into%20crisis.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Findia-us-pannun-nijjar-foreign-media%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Navigating%20PM-KISAN%3A%20A%20Deep%20Dive%20into%20Digital%20Challenges%20Faced%20by%20Farmers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F08200430%2Fimage1-2.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20PM-KISAN%20Samman%20Nidhi%20Scheme%2C%20initiated%20in%202019%2C%20serves%20as%20a%20crucial%20financial%20support%20system%20for%20Indian%20farmers%2C%20offering%20an%20annual%20Rs%206%2C000%20subsidy%20distributed%20in%20three%20instalments%20directly%20to%20their%20bank%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllocating%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fbudgets%2Fparliament%2Fdemand-for-grants-2023-24-analysis-agriculture-and-farmers-welfare%5C%22%3E50%25%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%20and%20Farmers%20Welfare%E2%80%99s%20budget%20to%20the%20PMKISAN%20scheme%20in%202022-23%20and%202023-24%3C%2Fa%3E%20underscores%20the%20high%20priority%20the%20Union%20government%20places%20on%20the%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2022%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Agriculture%20and%20Farmers%20Welfare%2C%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20introduced%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1959461%5C%22%3EAI%20Chatbot%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20PMKISAN%20Scheme.%20This%20chatbot%2C%20among%20other%20functions%2C%20aims%20to%20provide%20farmers%20with%20prompt%2C%20clear%20and%20accurate%20responses%20to%20their%20queries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20discuss%20the%20obstacles%20encountered%20by%20those%20using%20the%20scheme%20within%20its%20digital%20framework.%20We%20trace%20changes%20in%20two%20specific%20aspects%20of%20the%20digital%20framework%3A%20access%20to%20information%2C%20and%20changing%20compliances.%20The%20changes%20in%20both%20aspects%20since%202019%20impact%20not%20just%20%E2%80%98entitlement%20holders%E2%80%99%20experience%20of%20the%20scheme%2C%20but%20also%20potentially%20hamper%20the%20seamless%20flow%20of%20benefits.%20Using%20case%20studies%20gathered%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20(AP)%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Telangana%2C%20we%20illustrate%20the%20struggles%20of%20farmers%20and%20local%20officials%20in%20navigating%20PMKISAN%E2%80%99s%20digital%20landscape.%20This%20journey%20underscores%20the%20necessity%20for%20streamlined%20and%20accessible%20information%20systems%20to%20ensure%20any%20welfare%20programme%E2%80%99s%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccess%20to%20information%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20begin%20with%20the%20story%20of%20Pongo%20Donno%2C%20an%20Adivasi%20farmer%20from%20Odisha%2C%20whose%20journey%20to%20uncover%20his%20PMKISAN%20status%20illustrates%20how%20changes%20in%20the%20system%20have%20transformed%20his%20efforts%20to%20access%20this%20information%20over%20time.%20Donno%E2%80%99s%20primary%20concern%20is%20to%20stay%20informed%20about%20his%20payment%20status%2C%20the%20associated%20bank%20accounts%2C%20entitled%20and%20received%20instalments%2C%20as%20well%20as%20reasons%20for%20non-payment%20if%20any%20instalment%20is%20missed.%20This%20information%20is%20valuable%20for%20farmers%2C%20and%20is%20also%20the%20basic%20expectation%20from%20any%20portal%20providing%20information%20on%20a%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202019%2C%20the%20essential%20requirement%20for%20farmers%20%E2%80%93%20understanding%20their%20PMKISAN%20status%20%E2%80%93%20has%20undergone%20four%20changes.%20Just%20as%20farmers%20and%20officials%20understood%20one%20change%2C%20another%20system%20emerged.%20In%20Donno%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20the%20initial%20process%20relied%20on%20Aadhaar%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmkisan.gov.in%2FBeneficiaryStatus_New.aspx%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98KNOW%20YOUR%20STATUS%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Formerly%20%E2%80%98Beneficiary%20Status%E2%80%99)%20verification.%20Local%20officials%20would%20verify%20his%20PMKISAN%20status%20using%20his%20Aadhaar%20and%20provide%20the%20necessary%20information.%20They%20would%20also%20navigate%20through%20other%20details%20on%20PMKISAN%E2%80%99s%20Management%20Information%20System%20(MIS)%20to%20provide%20any%20missing%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Modi%20Government%20Has%20Underperformed%20in%20Developing%20the%20Rural%20Economy%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-government-underperform-developing-rural-economy%5C%22%3EThe%20Modi%20Government%20Has%20Underperformed%20in%20Developing%20the%20Rural%20Economy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20method%20later%20shifted%20towards%20verification%20through%20registration%20numbers%20or%20phone%20numbers%2C%20and%20later%20evolved%20to%20using%20registration%20numbers%20exclusively.%20For%20Donno%2C%20these%20methods%20proved%20futile%20as%20he%20lacked%20access%20to%20his%20registration%20number%20or%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20functioning%20phone%20number%20linked%20to%20his%20PMKISAN%20account%2C%20which%20is%20the%20situation%20for%20many%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20the%20system%20evolved%20to%20allow%20access%20to%20the%20registration%20number%20by%20using%20Aadhaar%20details.%20However%2C%20acquiring%20registration%20numbers%20remained%20a%20cumbersome%20task%20for%20Donno.%20He%20has%20to%20navigate%20the%20%E2%80%9Cknow%20your%20registration%20number%E2%80%9D%20option%20on%20MIS.%20Upon%20entering%20the%20OTP%20sent%20to%20his%20Aadhaar-linked%20mobile%2C%20Donno%20could%20access%20his%20PMKISAN%20registration%20number.%20This%20system%20proved%20less%20effective%20for%20farmers%20like%20him%20residing%20in%20areas%20with%20no%20network%20coverage%2C%20rendering%20the%20Aadhaar-phone%20link%20insignificant.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20phone%20number%20linked%20with%20the%20PMKISAN%20account%20option%20offered%20little%20help%20to%20Donno%20due%20to%20the%20frequent%20non-functionality%20of%20his%20mobile.%20The%20option%20of%20a%20simple%20paper%20trail%20would%20have%20resolved%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20farmers%20like%20Donno.%20This%20holds%20true%20for%20many%20entitlement-holders%20that%20reside%20in%20remote%2C%20network-poor%20areas%2C%20especially%20tribal%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmkisan.gov.in%2FDocuments%2FRevisedPM-KISANOperationalGuidelines(English).pdf%5C%22%3EPMKISAN%20operational%20guidelines%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%98beneficiary%20lists%E2%80%99%20should%20be%20posted%20at%20Panchayats%20for%20transparency.%20States%2FUTs%20should%20send%20SMS%20notifications%20to%20beneficiaries%20upon%20benefit%20sanction.%20But%20such%20measures%20are%20rarely%20followed.%20Even%20when%20the%20beneficiary%20lists%20are%20showcased%2C%20they%20lack%20payment%20details%20or%20reasons%20for%20non-payment%2C%20resulting%20in%20their%20ineffectiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChallenges%20with%20changing%20compliances%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20changes%20in%20the%20compliance%20structure%20of%20PMKISAN%20fund%20transfers%20also%20significantly%20impacted%20farmers%20like%20%E2%80%98Korra%20Jimbo%E2%80%99%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Originally%20registering%20in%202019%20without%20submitting%20his%20Aadhaar%2C%20Jimbo%20faced%20halted%20payments%20post%20the%20third%20instalment%20due%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmkisan.gov.in%2FDocuments%2FRevisedFAQ.pdf%5C%22%3Enewly-mandatory%20Aadhaar%20authentication%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Cross-verifying%20Aadhaar%20names%20with%20the%20PMKISAN%20list%20caused%20nationwide%20payment%20disruptions%2C%20leaving%20over%2097%2C000%20farmers%20in%20AP%20unpaid%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20a%202021%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Flibtech.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2FAP_PM_Kisan_Sep21.pdf%5C%22%3ELibTech%20India%20study%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompliance%20evolution%20didn%E2%80%99t%20halt%20there.%20In%20December%202021%2C%20E-Kyc%20emerged%20on%20ground%2C%20requiring%20farmers%20to%20submit%20biometrics%20for%20Aadhaar%20authentication%20either%20at%20the%20geographically%20scarce%20Customer%20Service%20Centre%20points%20or%20through%20the%20PMKISAN%20website%20via%20linked%20phone%20numbers%2C%20challenging%20those%20with%20unlinked%20Aadhaar-phone%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20came%20across%20several%20instances%20of%20farmers%20meeting%20the%20mandatory%20criteria%20of%20a%20bank%20account%20registered%20for%20Aadhaar-based%20payments%2C%20completed%20EKyc%2C%20and%20proper%20land%20seeding%20status%2C%20who%20faced%20challenges%20in%20receiving%20PMKISAN%20payments.%20Investigations%20showed%20their%20instalments%20were%20halted%20citing%20vague%20reasons%20like%20%E2%80%9CUntraceable%20Beneficiary%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%98Old%20district%20to%20new%20district%20transfer%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20lacked%20clarity%20on%20the%20specific%20reasons%20and%20resolutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20from%20Account%20Based%20payment%20to%20Aadhaar%20Based%20Payment%20System%20(ABPS)%20in%20March%202022%20further%20complicated%20matters.%20Mangiben%E2%80%99s%20case%20from%20Gujarat%20illustrates%20how%20the%20transition%20from%20a%20simple%20account%20transfer%20system%20to%20the%20ABPS%20in%20PMKISAN%20caused%20problems.%20Despite%20previously%20receiving%20funds%20in%20a%20known%20bank%20account%2C%20Mangiben%20missed%20her%20last%20two%20payments%20without%20explanation.%20ABPS%20requires%20farmers%E2%80%99%20bank%20accounts%20to%20be%20linked%20with%20Aadhaar%20and%20the%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(NPCI)%20mapper.%20However%2C%20for%20farmers%20who%20are%20not%20eligible%20for%20ABPS%2C%20the%20MIS%20incorrectly%20displays%20%E2%80%98Aadhaar%20not%20linked%20to%20Bank%20account%2C%E2%80%99%20leading%20to%20confusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELogin%20procedures%20for%20officials%20facilitating%20PMKISAN%20implementation%20have%20also%20evolved%2C%20from%20a%20straightforward%20user%20ID%20and%20password%20process%20to%20including%20OTPs.%20The%20Agricultural%20Department%20limited%20logins%20to%20NIC-registered%20officials%2C%20who%20were%20directed%20to%20download%20Kavach%2C%20an%20app%20generating%20OTPs%20for%20each%20login%20which%20was%20later%20rolled%20back.%20This%20convoluted%20procedure%20discouraged%20regular%20logins%20to%20address%20problems%20by%20local%20officials%2C%20further%20worsening%20challenges%20for%20vulnerable%20farmers.%20Though%20no%20clarity%20exists%20about%20the%20rationale%20behind%20the%20system%20changes%2C%20insights%20from%20official%20interviews%20suggest%20these%20modifications%20aim%20to%20prevent%20wrongful%20inclusions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20as%20we%20acknowledge%20the%20complex%20challenges%20posed%20by%20PMKISAN%E2%80%99s%20evolving%20compliance%20landscape%2C%20the%20introduction%20of%20technological%20solutions%20that%20reduce%20the%20hardships%20to%20people%20are%20welcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20recognise%20that%20vulnerable%20sections%2C%20as%20highlighted%20in%20this%20article%2C%20often%20face%20digital%20disadvantages%20due%20to%20various%20reasons.%20Therefore%2C%20while%20embracing%20technological%20advancements%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20not%20to%20compromise%20offline%20systems%20that%20have%20traditionally%20served%20as%20a%20lifeline%20for%20those%20with%20limited%20digital%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20integration%20of%20AI%20Chatbots%20should%20complement%2C%20not%20replace%2C%20existing%20offline%20mechanisms.%20For%20farmers%20like%20Donno%20and%20Jimbo%2C%20grappling%20with%20network%20issues%20and%20changing%20digital%20requirements%2C%20maintaining%20robust%20offline%20support%20is%20essential.%20By%20adopting%20a%20balanced%20approach%20that%20harnesses%20the%20power%20of%20technology%20while%20safeguarding%20the%20accessibility%20of%20offline%20systems%2C%20we%20can%20ensure%20not%20only%20that%20the%20benefits%20of%20social%20welfare%20programmes%20reach%20every%20corner%20of%20society%20but%20also%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20people%20to%20access%20their%20entitlements%2C%20leaving%20no%20one%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EChakradhar%20Buddha%20and%20B.D.S.%20Kishore%20are%20affiliated%20with%20LibTech%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701325889000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F08200430%2Fimage1-2.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnavigating-pm-kisan-a-deep-dive-into-digital-challenges-faced-by-farmers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20embracing%20technological%20advancements%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20not%20to%20compromise%20offline%20systems%20that%20have%20traditionally%20served%20as%20a%20lifeline%20for%20those%20with%20limited%20digital%20access.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnavigating-pm-kisan-a-deep-dive-into-digital-challenges-faced-by-farmers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nepal%20Becomes%20First%20South%20Asian%20Country%20to%20Officially%20Recognise%20a%20Queer%20Marriage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F12171059%2FLGBT.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ENepal%20has%20become%20the%20first%20South%20Asian%20country%20to%20officially%20register%20a%20queer%20marriage.%20The%20registration%20took%20place%20in%20Lamjung%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkathmandupost.com%2Fgandaki-province%2F2023%2F11%2F30%2Fnepal-becomes-second-country-in-asia-to-register-same-sex-marriage%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Kathmandu%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty-seven-year%20old%20Surendra%20Pandey%20and%2037-year-old%20Maya%20Gurung%20registered%20their%20marriage%20five%20years%20after%20getting%20married%20at%20a%20temple%2C%20the%20portal%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20met%20in%20a%20restaurant%20and%20immediately%20liked%20each%20other.%20After%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20of%20courtship%2C%20we%20moved%20in%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Maya%20about%20their%20meeting%20around%20nine%20years%20ago.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20our%20family%20and%20society%20did%20not%20accept%20us.%20We%20then%20moved%20to%20Kathmandu.%20Although%20we%20got%20married%20in%20a%20temple%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20our%20marriage%20was%20not%20legally%20recognised.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDordi%20Rural%20Municipality%20chairman%20Yuvaraj%20Adhikari%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kathmandu%20Post%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20registration%20request%20had%20been%20filed%20a%20week