Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20company%20has%20a%20customer%20base%20of%20more%20than%20250%20subscribers%20with%20over%202%2C000%20downloads%20of%20the%20application%20per%20day.%20They%20also%20have%20collaborations%20with%2070%20toy%20companies%20where%20they%20source%20their%20toys.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20these%20250%20subscribers%20is%20Rahul%20Bhauwala%20from%20Mumbai%20who%20rents%20toys%20for%20his%206-year-old.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20working%20professional%20and%20I%20hardly%20get%20any%20time%20to%20go%20out%20and%20spend%20hours%20looking%20for%20and%20buying%20toys.%20I%20could%20use%20that%20precious%20time%20to%20play%20with%20my%20child%20instead.%20This%20is%20why%20I%20love%20using%20The%20EleFant%20app.%20They%20have%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20toys%20which%20are%20categorised%20as%20per%20age.%20The%20products%20are%20very%20well-packaged%20and%20my%20son%20loved%20opening%20them%20as%20it%20looked%20like%20a%20present%20to%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20aim%20to%20establish%20a%20circular%20economy%20where%20toys%20are%20reused%20repeatedly.%20This%20not%20only%20cuts%20costs%20but%20also%20benefits%20the%20environment.%20Considering%20how%20quickly%20kids%20outgrow%20things%2C%20toys%20often%20end%20up%20in%20landfills%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPocket-friendly%20for%20parents%20and%20fun%20for%20kids%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20habit%20of%20reusing%20and%20thrifting%20might%20have%20started%20trending%20recently%2C%20if%20we%20look%20back%20to%20our%20childhood%2C%20sharing%20children%E2%80%99s%20belongings%20has%20always%20been%20part%20of%20our%20culture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20pass%20down%20our%20toys%20and%20clothes%20to%20our%3Cem%3E%20chachi%2C%20mami%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20(aunts)%20kids.%20However%2C%20with%20the%20nuclear%20family%20setup%2C%20this%20trend%20has%20declined.%20I%20think%20